questioned%20why%20businessman%20Gautam%20Adani's%20brother%20left%20India%20during%20the%20%26quot%3BAmrit%20Kaal%26quot%3B%20period%2C%20referring%20to%20reports%20of%20Indians%20obtaining%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20passports%26quot%3B%20in%20Cyprus.%20The%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20passport%26quot%3B%20scheme%2C%20which%20facilitated%20Cypriot%20citizenship%20for%20financially%20prominent%20individuals%2C%20was%20introduced%20in%202007.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20BJP%20criticized%20the%20Congress-led%20UPA%20government%20for%20creating%20a%20haven%20for%20tax%20evaders%20through%20the%20India-Cyprus%20tax%20treaty.%20BJP%20claimed%20that%20they%20took%20decisive%20action%20to%20overhaul%20the%20treaty%2C%20shifting%20the%20taxation%20of%20capital%20gains%20to%20the%20source%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AI%20is%20fueling%20transformative%20new%20brain-health%20technology%20to%20detect%20and%20prevent%20cognitive%20decline%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221969%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20doctor%20looks%20at%20a%20patient's%20brain%20scan%20on%20a%20screen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6553cffa36d588dc55d01f77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221522%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Brookes%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20global%20population%20is%20aging%2C%20presenting%20new%20challenges%20related%20to%20cognitive%20decline.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20startup%20is%20building%20an%20AI%20tool%20to%20identify%20potential%20cognitive%20decline%20based%20on%20driving%20behavior.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnother%20is%20developing%20AI%20tools%20to%20detect%20and%20prevent%20postoperative%20delirium%20before%20it%20occurs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20story%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fhow-emerging-tech-is-changing-everything%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Emerging%20Tech%20Is%20Changing%20Everything%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20exploring%20the%20transformative%20impact%20of%20tech%20innovations%20across%20industries.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20global%20population%20ages%2C%20the%20challenges%20associated%20with%20cognitive%20decline%20become%20more%20prominent.%20Beyond%20economic%20implications%20and%20labor%20shortages%2C%20issues%20such%20as%20dementia%20and%20postoperative%20delirium%20%E2%80%94%20a%20debilitating%20condition%20associated%20with%20cognitive%20decline%2C%20dementia%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC9395738%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eincreased%20risk%20of%20mortality%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20present%20immediate%2C%20real-world%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20cutting-edge%20technologies%20are%20emerging%20to%20address%20these%20challenges%2C%20with%20companies%20developing%20novel%20tools%20designed%20to%20detect%2C%20prevent%2C%20and%20manage%20cognitive%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EImproving%20road%20safety%20with%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Japan%2C%20where%2029%25%20of%20the%20population%20is%20over%2065%20and%20more%20than%206%20million%20people%20live%20with%20dementia%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20an%20aging%20society%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5g-technology-safer-roads-virginia-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eroad%20safety%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20growing%20concern.%20To%20address%20this%20issue%2C%20the%20UK%20software%20company%20Mind%20Foundry%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20insurance%20giant%20Aioi%20Nissay%20Dowa%20Insurance%2C%20is%20building%20artificial-intelligence%20tools%20to%20detect%20cognitive%20decline%20in%20older%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20an%20analysis%20of%20ANDI's%20extensive%20dashcam%20data%20covering%209%20million%20miles%20of%20road%20and%20using%20Mind%20Foundry's%20machine-learning%20models%2C%20the%20two%20companies%20have%20developed%20an%20AI%20system%20to%20identify%20subtle%20patterns%20indicative%20of%20cognitive%20decline.%20This%20not%20only%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20aid%20in%20preventing%20road%20accidents%20but%20also%20allows%20for%20personalized%20insurance%20plans%20based%20on%20a%20person's%20cognitive%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20identifying%20the%205%25%20of%20customers%20responsible%20for%2050%25%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20claims%2C%20the%20technology%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20significantly%20alter%20how%20insurers%20understand%20and%20manage%20risk%2C%20the%20companies%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTraditionally%2C%20insurers%20have%20relied%20heavily%20on%20details%20such%20as%20the%20type%20of%20car%2C%20driver%20age%2C%20and%20location%20to%20predict%20those%20likely%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20most%20serious%20accidents%20and%20to%20set%20insurance%20premiums%2C%26quot%3B%20Mind%20Foundry%20CEO%20Brian%20Mullins%20said.%20%26quot%3BMind%20Foundry's%20AI%20system%20goes%20much%20further%20in%20order%20to%20understand%20more%20subtle%2C%20hidden%20patterns%20in%20the%20data%20that%20can%20help%20to%20underwrite%20these%20risks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20system%20studied%20numerous%20behavior%20patterns%2C%20such%20as%20harsh%20braking%2C%20erratic%20swerving%2C%20and%20sudden%20acceleration%20among%20drivers%20who%20had%20been%20in%20the%20most%20severe%2C%20large-loss%20accidents.%20It%20then%20analyzed%20similar%20patterns%20among%20a%20different%20set%20of%20older%20drivers%20to%20identify%20which%20risk%20factors%20could%20predict%20cognitive%20decline%20before%20it%20became%20dangerous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMullins%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BTo%20ensure%20ethical%20practices%2C%20humans%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20decision-making%20process.%20AI%20doesn't%20make%20the%20decision.%20Rather%2C%20it%20informs%20the%20insurance%20experts%20about%20the%20potential%20customer's%20risks%20before%20determining%20the%20coverage%20and%20pricing%20for%20that%20individual.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIdentifying%20postoperative%20delirium%20before%20it%20hits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EElsewhere%2C%20PIPRA%20AG%2C%20a%20medtech%20startup%20in%20Zurich%2C%20has%20developed%20an%20AI-based%20tool%20called%20PIPRA%20to%20predict%20postoperative%20delirium%20in%20people%20over%2060%20undergoing%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPOD%20is%20a%20terrible%20condition%2C%20with%20symptoms%20that%20include%20agitation%20or%20profound%20inactivity%2C%20as%20well%20as%20changes%20to%20a%20person's%20attention%2C%20awareness%2C%20and%20cognitive%20ability%2C%26quot%3B%20PIPRA%20CEO%20John%20Klepper%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20also%20associated%20with%20an%20increase%20in%20postsurgery%20falls%2C%20longer%20hospital%20stays%2C%20increased%20nursing-home%20admissions%2C%20hospital%20readmissions%2C%20cognitive%20decline%2C%20dementia%2C%20and%20increased%20mortality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20Klepper's%20mother's%20experience%20after%20surgery%20that%20led%20him%20to%20his%20research.%20%26quot%3BFor%20days%2C%20she%20saw%20monsters%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20hospital%20walls%20and%20thought%20the%20hospital%20staff%20were%20trying%20to%20kill%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20she%20was%20fortunate%20enough%20to%20'recover%20fully%2C'%20she%20has%20a%20type%20of%20PTSD%20from%20the%20experience%20and%2C%20to%20this%20day%2C%20is%20still%20terrified%20of%20hospitals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPIPRA's%20predictive%20tool%20uses%20AI%20algorithms%20that%20analyze%20clinical%20information%20routinely%20collected%20by%20healthcare%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20an%20ideal%20world%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20see%20our%20solution%20being%20integrated%20into%20healthcare%20facilities%20in%20every%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Klepper%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20way%2C%20we%20will%20be%20creating%20measurable%20global%20impact%20and%20improving%20and%20saving%20the%20lives%20of%20millions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPOD%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20and%20most%20expensive%20problems%20in%20healthcare.%20For%20scale%2C%20POD%20costs%2060%25%20more%20to%20healthcare%20providers%20than%20diabetes%20and%20affects%20at%20least%2060%20million%20around%20the%20world%20each%20year.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20often%20ignored.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ETech%20can%20be%20proactive%2C%20too%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECognitive-fitness%20tech%20doesn't%20always%20have%20to%20be%20reactive.%20Incisiv%2C%20a%20neurotech%20company%20founded%20by%20Cathy%20Craig%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20Royal%20Academy%20of%20Engineering%20Enterprise%20Hub%20in%20London%2C%20focuses%20on%20monitoring%20neural%20fitness%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0how%20well%20the%20brain%20controls%20movement%20and%20makes%20decisions%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0using%20virtual-reality%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20applications%20in%20sports%20and%20beyond%2C%20Incisiv's%20technology%20has%20been%20adopted%20by%20world-leading%20sports%20teams%2C%20including%20the%20Italian%20Rugby%20Federation%20and%20the%20Elite%20Ice%20Hockey%20League.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20traditional%20concussion%20assessments%2C%20which%20involve%20questionnaires%20or%20symptom%20checklists%2C%20Incisiv's%20virtual-reality%20tests%20provide%20a%20more%20nuanced%20understanding%20of%20brain%20health.%20By%20measuring%20players'%20interactions%20with%20and%20processing%20of%20information%20at%20a%20finer%20level%2C%20the%20technology%20allows%20for%20a%20comprehensive%20assessment%20of%20cognitive%20function.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIncisiv%20aims%20to%20bring%20this%20technology%20into%20homes%2C%20enabling%20parents%20to%20monitor%20their%20children's%20brain%20health%20from%20a%20young%20age.%20In%20the%20context%20of%20children's%20sports%2C%20the%20tech%20can%20look%20at%20the%20brain%20before%20and%20after%20a%20game%20and%20flag%20any%20discrepancies%2C%20allowing%20parents%20and%20coaches%20to%20ensure%20safe%20playing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20convergence%20of%20AI%2C%20medical%20technology%2C%20and%20neurotech%20is%20leading%20the%20fight%20against%20cognitive%20decline.%20From%20detecting%20subtle%20patterns%20in%20driving%20behavior%20to%20predicting%20postoperative%20delirium%20and%20monitoring%20neural%20fitness%2C%20these%20technologies%20offer%20a%20glimpse%20into%20a%20future%20where%20cognitive%20decline%20is%20not%20just%20managed%20but%20also%20prevented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20these%20innovations%20continue%20to%20evolve%2C%20the%20potential%20to%20transform%20individual%20lives%20and%20alleviate%20the%20strain%20on%20healthcare%20systems%20globally%20becomes%20increasingly%20evident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdetecting-and-preventing-cognitive-decline-with-ai-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700056978000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6553d01d22cf74a573971d83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdetecting-and-preventing-cognitive-decline-with-ai-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AI%2C%20medtech%2C%20and%20neurotech%20are%20converging%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20preventing%20cognitive%20decline.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Hazel%20Davis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdetecting-and-preventing-cognitive-decline-with-ai-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Myanmar%20Rebels%20Claim%20Entire%20Battalion%20Comprising%20100%2B%20Soldiers%20Has%20Surrendered%22%2C%22content%22%3A%2