s%20shared%20tips%20and%20best%20practices.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EYouTube%20exec%20Bridget%20Dolan%20spoke%20about%20why%20the%20platform%20is%20betting%20on%20short-video%20to%20drive%20shopping.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BShoppable%20short-form%20video%20is%20on%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20Dolan%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20livestream%20shopping%20is%20booming%20in%20Asia%2C%20the%20trend%20has%20yet%20to%20make%20waves%20in%20the%20US.%20Platforms%20like%20TikTok%20and%20YouTube%20are%20still%20betting%20on%20e-commerce%2C%20but%20have%20instead%20shifted%20some%20focus%20toward%20short%20videos%20driving%20sales%20instead%20of%20hours-long%20livestreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20latest%20CreatorIQ%20Connect%20conference%20series%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20the%20marketing%20platform%20hosted%20panels%20with%20industry%20professionals%20like%20Michelle%20Miller%2C%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20global%20marketing%20at%20K18%3B%20Bridget%20Dolan%2C%20global%20managing%20director%20of%20YouTube%20Shopping%3B%20and%20Jackie%20Pimentel%2C%20senior%20global%20marketing%20director%20at%20Meta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDolan%20spoke%20about%20how%20the%20tech%20giant%20is%20thinking%20about%20social%20shopping%20and%20why%20her%20team%20is%20betting%20on%20short%20videos%20to%20drive%20sales%20over%20livestreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShoppable%20short-form%20video%20is%20on%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20Dolan%20said%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.creatoriq.com%2Fconnect2023-creators-and-online-shopping%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20speaking%20on%20a%20panel%20about%20creators%20and%20online%20shopping%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20over%20150%20billion%20views%20in%202022%20of%20videos%20with%20products%20tagged%20%E2%80%94%20shoppable%20videos%20on%20YouTube.%20Shopping%20shorts%20are%20growing%20a%20lot%20faster%20than%20shorts%20are%20growing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDolan%20added%20that%20shopping%20content%20performs%20best%20on%20YouTube%20when%20it%20doesn't%20look%20overly%20staged%2C%20or%20have%20a%20high%20production%20value%2C%20and%20highlights%20a%20single%20product%20or%20brand%20in%20a%20vertical%2015-to-30-second%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20basically%20like%20a%20quick%20review%20of%20why%20this%20product%20is%20amazing%2C%26quot%3B%20Dolan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYouTube%20has%20over%20150%20brands%20as%20part%20of%20the%20platform's%20new%20affiliate%20program.%20To%20join%20as%20a%20brand%2C%20the%20company%20must%20have%20a%20relationship%20with%20affiliate%20networks%20Rakuten%2C%20Impact%2C%20or%20CJ%20Affiliate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYouTube%20first%20began%20quietly%20testing%20shopping%20tools%20in%202021%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbridget-dolan-david-katz-leading-youtube-social-commerce-push-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eproduct%20pins%20with%20a%20small%20group%20of%20creators%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20affiliate%20program%2C%20which%20launched%20in%20June%2C%20lets%20creators%20earn%20commissions%20when%20they%20tag%20products%20in%20their%20videos%2C%20from%20shorts%20and%20long-form%20content%20to%20livestreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWooing%20creators%20and%20best%20practices%20to%20drive%20sales%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20every%20product%20%E2%80%94%20or%20creator%20%E2%80%94%20can%20drive%20e-commerce%20sales.%20Instead%20of%20leaning%20on%20top%20creators%20like%20MrBeast%2C%20YouTube%20is%20working%20with%20a%20group%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCkYQyvc_i9hXEo4xic9Hh2g%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etech%2C%20fashion%2C%20and%20beauty%20influencers%20to%20drive%20its%20shopping%20efforts%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B150%2C000%20or%201%20million%20subscribers%20on%20YouTube%20are%20hard%20earned%2C%26quot%3B%20Dolan%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20does%20not%20come%20fast%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20come%20easy%2C%20but%20when%20they%20build%20an%20audience%20like%20that%2C%20they%20really%20listen%20and%20they%20have%20that%20trust.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20worked%20are%20exclusive%20drops%2C%20as%20well%20as%20concert%20and%20sports%20team%20apparel%2C%20Dolan%20said.%20Throughout%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-partners-with-coachella-to-sell-merch-livestream-shopping-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EYouTube%20partnered%20with%20both%20Coachella%20and%20the%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20NFL%20to%20sell%20exclusive%20merch%2C%20and%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dc9f96W4TOXQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehired%20creators%20to%20drive%20buzz%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20the%20launch%20of%20Google's%20Pixel%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20YouTube%20invited%20100%20top%20beauty%20and%20fashion%20creators%20to%20its%20LA%20office%20to%20shop%20from%20brands%20available%20on%20the%20affiliate%20program%20and%20get%20tips%20from%20execs%20on%20how%20to%20sell%20in%20an%20authentic%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20they%20love%20the%20brand%20deals%2C%20and%20they%20love%20having%20those%20relationships%2C%20but%20this%20is%20the%20opposite%2C%26quot%3B%20Dolan%20said%20of%20affiliate%20marketing.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20them%20coming%20up%20with%20what%20they'd%20like%20to%20talk%20about.%20They're%20creating%20on%20their%20own.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-betting-on-short-form-video-to-drive-social-commerce-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700055358000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6553d23c22cf74a57397232a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-betting-on-short-form-video-to-drive-social-commerce-20