ss%20%E2%80%94%20or%20their%20ability%20to%20repay%20debt.%20Who%20can%20borrow%20how%20much%2C%20and%20at%20what%20cost%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20all%20very%20clearly%20understood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20US%20is%20the%20world's%20biggest%20economy%2C%20with%20the%20biggest%20businesses%2C%20and%20is%20a%20magnet%20for%20global%20investors.%20Such%20unrivaled%20economic%20muscle%20would%20mean%20the%20American%20government%20can%20borrow%20money%20much%20more%20cheaply%20than%20other%20sovereign%20entities%20%E2%80%94%20especially%2C%20emerging-market%20nations%20with%20weaker%20credit%20ratings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%20so%20we%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EUpside-down%20bond%20dynamics%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20surprising%20development%20that%20upends%20some%20of%20the%20bond%20world's%20time-honored%20conventions%2C%20the%20US%20government's%20borrowing%20costs%20have%20surged%20past%20those%20of%20developing%20nations%20with%20much%20poorer%20debt%20ratings%20such%20as%20Vietnam%2C%20Morocco%2C%20and%20Bulgaria.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20all%20due%20to%20the%20Federal%20Reserve's%20war%20on%20inflation%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20it%20raise%20rates%20at%20the%20sharpest%20pace%20since%20the%201980s.%20The%20Fed%20has%20lifted%20its%20benchmark%20rate%2C%20which%20forms%20the%20floor%20for%20all%20market%20interest%20rates%20by%20default%2C%20by%20more%20than%20500%20basis%20points%20over%20the%20past%2020%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that's%20driven%20up%20the%20rates%20on%20Treasury%20bonds%2C%20which%20represent%20the%20government's%20borrowing%20costs.%20Yields%20on%20benchmark%2010-year%20Treasurys%20have%20nearly%20tripled%20since%20the%20end%20of%202021%20to%20about%204.5%25.%20They%20have%20retreated%20from%20a%2016-year%20high%20of%20just%20above%205%25%20reached%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rate%20surged%20past%20the%20comparable%20measure%20in%20junk-rated%20Vietnam%20this%20year.%20Hanoi%20now%20pays%20only%20about%202.8%25%20to%20borrow%20money%20for%2010%20years%20in%20the%20local%20bond%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221159%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20bond%20yields%20have%20risen%20above%20junk-rated%20Vietnam's%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6554b2bc4ca513d82429a84a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22869%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20bond%20yields%20have%20risen%20above%20junk-rated%20Vietnam's%3Cp%3ETradingView%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ES%26amp%3BP%20Global%20ratings%20ranks%20Vietnam's%20debt%20at%20BB%2B%20%E2%80%94%20which%20the%20credit%20assessor%20defines%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bhighest%20speculative%20grade%26quot%3B.%20The%20US%20is%20rated%20AA%2B%2C%20which%20reflects%20a%20very%20strong%20capacity%20to%20meet%20financial%20commitments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20even%20sure%20what%20to%20say%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20Jeff%20Weniger%2C%20head%20of%20equities%20at%20WisdomTree%20Asset%20Management%2C%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJeffWeniger%2Fstatus%2F1719099134286631246%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20post%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20highlighting%20the%20rise%20in%20American%20bond%20yields%20above%20Vietnamese%20equivalents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%2010-year%20yields%20are%20now%20also%20higher%20than%20those%20in%20emerging%20markets%20such%20as%20Morocco%20and%20Bulgaria.%20Similar%20rates%20are%20at%20just%203.8%25%20in%20Greece%2C%20the%20economy%20at%20the%20center%20of%20Europe's%20sovereign%20debt%20crisis%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20and%20needed%20multiple%20European%20Union%20bailouts%20in%20the%20following%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20US%20yields%20also%20reflect%20investor%20concerns%20about%20America's%20deteriorating%20public%20finances.%20US%20total%20debt%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20in%20the%20past%20decade%20to%20%2433.7%20trillion%2C%20or%20more%20than%2025%25%20of%20GDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoody's%20Investors%20Service%20lowered%20its%20outlook%20for%20the%20US%20credit%20rating%20last%20week%20to%20negative%20from%20stable%2C%20citing%20the%20growing%20mountain%20of%20debt%20and%20high%20interest%20rates.%20In%20August%2C%20Fitch%20Ratings%20downgraded%20its%20rating%20for%20long-term%20US%20debt%20to%20AA%2B%20from%20AAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbonds-bonkers-us-debt-costs-exceed-vietnam-morocco-bulgaria-junk-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700054547000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6554888a36d588dc55d08dda%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fbonds-bonkers-us-debt-costs-exceed-vietnam-morocco-bulgaria-junk-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20its%20AA%2B%20credit%20rating%2C%20the%20US%20now%20pays%20more%20to%20borrow%20than%20countries%20like%20junk-rated%20Vietnam%20after%20bond%20yields%20nearly%20tripled%20since%20late%202021.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22avarma%40insider.com%20(Anil%20Varma)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fbonds-bonkers-us-debt-costs-exceed-vietnam-morocco-bulgaria-junk-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22For%20Tunnel%20Rescue%2C%20Call%20Made%20To%20Firm%20That%20Saved%20Thai%20Children%20From%20Cave%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20landslide%20and%20technical%20issues%20hampered%20rescue%20efforts%2C%20three%20special%20aircraft%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20are%20transporting%20a%2025-tonne%20ray%20of%20hope%20for%20the%2040%20labourers%20who%20have%20been%20trapped%20in%20a%20tunnel%20in%20Uttarakhand%20for%20over%20three%20days%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecial%20teams%20from%20Thailand%20and%20Norway%2C%20including%20the%20one%20that%20had%20helped%20save%20the%20children%20stuck%20in%20a%20cave%20in%20Thailand%20in%202018%2C%20have%20also%20been%20roped%20in%20to%20aid%20in%20the%20rescue%20of%20the%20labourers%20who%20were%20trapped%20after%20the%20under-construction%20tunnel%20collapsed%20on%20the%20Char%20Dham%20route%20in%20Uttarkashi%20early%20on%20Sunday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20special%20machine%2C%20which%20is%20being%20brought%20to%20the%20site%20from%20Delhi%2C%20can%20penetrate%204-5%20metres%20of%20debris%20in%20an%20hour%20and%2C%20if%20all%20goes%20well%2C%20help%20push%20the%20rescue%20pipe%20to%20the%20spot%20where%20the%20labourers%20are%20trapped%20in%2010-12%20hours.%20The%20pipe%20has%20a%20diameter%20of%20900%20mm%2C%20which%20will%20be%20enough%20for%20the%20men%20to%20squeeze%20through%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20the%20machine%20was%20expected%20to%20arrive%20late%20in%20the%20evening%20and%20it%20could%20be%20installed%20and%20work%20could%20begin%20a%20few%20hours%20after%20it%20arrives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECave%20Expertise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeams%20involved%20in%20the%20rescue%20have%20contacted%20a%20company%20from%20Thailand%20which%20had%20helped%20save%20a%20junior%20association%20football%20team%20that%20was%20trapped%20in%20Tham%20Luang%20Nang%20Non%2C%20a%20cave%20system%20in%20Chiang%20Rai%20province%2C%20northern%20Thailand%2C%20in%202018.%20That%20rescue%20effort%20took%20over%20a%20week%20and%20involved%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20people%20and%2C%20officials%20said%2C%20the%20company's%20expertise%20will%20be%20invaluable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHelp%20is%20also%20being%20taken%20from%20the%20Norwegian%20Geotechnical%20Institute%20for%20suggestions%20on%20how%20to%20carry%20out%20operations%20inside%20the%20tunnel.%20Such%20suggestions%20are%20also%20being%20taken%20from%20experts%20in%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20and%20bodies%20affiliated%20to%20it%20such%20as%20Rail%20Vikas%20Nigam%20Limited%2C%20Rail%20India%20Technical%20and%20Economic%20Service%20(RITES)%20and%20Indian%20Railway%20Construction%20International%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnshu%20Manish%20Khalkho%2C%20Director%2C%20National%20Highways%20%26amp%3B%20Infrastructure%20Development%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20machine%20is%20on%20the%20way%20and%20should%20arrive%20soon.%20In%20three-four%20hours%2C%20we%20can%20begin%20work%20with%20it.%20Debris%20is%20being%20removed%20but%20some%20of%20it%20is%20being%20replaced%20by%20more%20falling%20debris.%20So%2C%20that%20is%20not%20our%20focus.%20We%20are%20trying%20to%20push%20the%20pipe%20through.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Labourers%20Okay'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20new%20machine%20can%20push%20the%20pipe%20about%203-4%20metres%20in%20an%20hour%20and%20we%20can%20finish%20the%20work%20in%2010-12%20hours%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20depends%20on%20what%20machines%20are%20stuck%20inside.%20The%20labourers%20are%20fine%2C%20they%20are%20getting%20food%20and%20their%20families%20and%20officials%20are%20speaking%20to%20them%20to%20keep%20their%20morale%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khalkho%20said%20they%20have%20a%20backup%20plan%20in%20place%20even%20if%20this%20machine%20does%20not%20work%20and%20it%20is%20very%20hard%20to%20put%20a%20timeframe%20on%20the%20rescue%20plan.%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20us%20are%20as%20worried%20as%20the%20families%20of%20the%20labourers%20and%20no%20one%20is%20resting%20until%20we%20rescue%20our%20brothers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20family%20members%20and%20other%20labourers%20also%20held%20a%20protest%20near%20the%20site%20over%20the%20delay%20in%20rescuing%20the%20trapped%20men.%20Mr%20Khalkho%20said%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20the%20protesters%20and%20claimed%20they%20have%20understood%20the%20situation%20and%20agreed%20to%20help%20in%20the%20rescue%20operation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20portion%20of%20the%204.5-km%20tunnel%20on%20the%20Brahmakhal-Yamunot