%20be%20under%20threat.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump's%20social%20media%20platform%2C%20Truth%20Social%2C%20has%20lost%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F1849635%2F000119312523276045%2Fd408563ds4a.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESEC%3C%2Fa%3E%20filings%20released%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETruth%20Social%20posted%20a%20net%20loss%20of%20almost%20%2423%20million%20for%20the%20first%20six%20months%20of%20the%20year%2C%20compared%20with%20a%20profit%20of%20almost%20%2429%20million%20for%20the%20same%20period%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20figures%20were%20contained%20in%20a%20securities%20filing%20made%20by%20Digital%20World%20Acquisition%20Corp%2C%20the%20special%20purpose%20acquisition%20company%2C%20or%20%26quot%3BSpac%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20plans%20to%20merge%20with%20Truth%20Social%20owner%20Trump%20Media%20and%20Technology%20Group%20(TMTG).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20merger%20has%20been%20delayed%20by%20setbacks%20and%20legal%20challenges%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20and%20the%20US%20securities%20regulator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDigital%20World%20has%20now%20asked%20investors%20to%20extend%20the%20deadline%20for%20the%20Truth%20Social%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Monday's%20filings%2C%20TMTG's%20independent%20accounting%20firm%20indicated%20that%20negative%20cash%20flows%20and%20recurring%20losses%20meant%20it%20had%20%26quot%3Bsubstantial%20doubt%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20company's%20financial%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20filings%20laid%20out%20risks%20facing%20TMTG%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20Truth%20Social%20fails%20to%20develop%20and%20maintain%20followers%20or%20a%20sufficient%20audience%2C%20if%20adverse%20trends%20develop%20in%20the%20social%20media%20platforms%20generally%2C%20or%20if%20President%20Trump%20were%20to%20cease%20to%20be%20able%20to%20devote%20substantial%20time%20to%20Truth%20Social%2C%20TMTG's%20business%