%20has%20no%20reason%20to%20believe%20the%20pitch%20won't%20play%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20ICC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20ICC's%20Playing%20Conditions%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20the%20host%20association%20is%20%26quot%3Bresponsible%20for%20the%20selection%20and%20preparation%20of%20the%20pitch%26quot%3B%20and%20there%20is%20no%20requirement%20that%20a%20knockout%20match%20must%20be%20played%20on%20fresh%20pitches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralian%20captain%20Pat%20Cummins%20also%20did%20not%20read%20too%20much%20into%20the%20pitch%20episode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20I%20saw%20that%20(the%20report)...%20obviously%20ICC%20have%20an%20independent%20pitch%20curator%20who%20manages%20that.%20So%20I'm%20sure%20they%20are%20making%20sure%20it's%20fair%20for%20both%20teams%2C%26quot%3B%20Cummins%20said%20ahead%20of%20Australia's%20semifinal%20against%20South%20Africa%20at%20Eden%20Gardens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20far%20this%20tournament%20that%20we've%20played%20on%2C%20I've%20not%20seen%20any%20issue%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Cummins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20semifinal%20of%20this%20tournament%2C%20India%20opted%20to%20bat%20first%20after%20winning%20the%20toss%20against%20New%20Zealand%20and%20made%20a%20strong%20start%20reaching%20150%20for%201%20in%2020%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20winners%20of%20this%20match%20will%20face%20either%20five-time%20champions%20Australia%20or%20South%20Africa%20in%20the%20title%20clash%20at%20Ahmedabad%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700052240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F2ka75mv_rohit-sharma-pitch-afp_625x300_15_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Falready-happened-a-couple-of-times-icc-issues-clarification-on