to%20take%20in.%20This%20carnage%20must%20be%20stopped%2C%20there%20must%20be%20a%20ceasefire%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22FootnoteAnchorToDOM%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frgupta.substack.com%2Fp%2Freflections-on-the-israel-palestine%23footnote-1-138856401%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E1%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20difficult%20not%20to%20have%20a%20strong%20visceral%20reaction%20to%20such%20suffering%3B%20however%2C%20I%20am%20conscious%20of%20my%20distance%20from%20this%20conflict%20in%20which%20all%20principal%20stakeholders%20have%20personally%20experienced%20loss%20at%20one%20time%20or%20the%20other.%20Some%20tentativeness%20is%20only%20fitting.%20I%20am%20not%20going%20to%20write%20about%20what%20was%20done%20or%20what%20should%20be%20done%20%E2%80%93%20there%20are%20very%20many%20columns%20and%20podcasts%20from%20more%20relevant%20people%20to%20read%20and%20listen%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20and%20large%2C%20the%20ones%20I%20most%20agree%20with%20converge%20on%20the%20following%20points%3A%20what%20Hamas%20did%20was%20an%20act%20of%20terrorism%20deserving%20of%20unequivocal%20condemnation%3B%20any%20meaningful%20discussion%20must%20be%20situated%20in%20the%20context%20and%20history%20of%20Israel%20and%20Palestine%2C%20which%20includes%20not%20just%20Jewish%20persecution%20but%20also%20the%20expulsion%20of%20Palestinians%20and%20their%20continued%20oppression%3B%20Israel%20cannot%20not%20go%20after%20Hamas%2C%20not%20least%20because%20the%20primary%20responsibility%20of%20any%20state%20is%20to%20provide%20security%20to%20its%20citizenry%20and%20its%20geopolitical%20context%20which%20requires%20establishing%20some%20manner%20of%20deterrence%20for%20such%20acts%3B%20but%20going%20after%20Hamas%20means%20targeted%20action%20instead%20of%20this%20unconscionable%20bombing%20of%20the%20entire%20Gaza%20strip%20which%20is%20leading%20to%20unacceptable%20civilian%20casualties%3B%20ultimately%2C%20the%20only%20lasting%20resolution%20will%20be%20political%2C%20which%20affords%20Palestinians%20dignity%20and%20agency%20instead%20of%20treating%20this%20as%20a%20security%20issue%20in%20perpetuity%3B%20and%20that%20Netanyahu%20is%20a%20tool%20responsible%20for%20propping%20up%20Hamas%20and%20for%20fomenting%20divisions%20in%20Israel%2C%20which%20made%20it%20susceptible%20to%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20column%20is%20thus%20not%20about%20the%20specifics%20of%20the%20Israel-Gaza%20situation%20but%20reflections%20brought%20on%20by%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20for%20me%2C%20the%20conflict%20has%20led%20to%20the%20collapse%20of%20any%20remaining%20delusions%20about%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20liberal%20world%20order.%20The%20basic%20premise%20of%20the%20liberal%20world%20order%20is%20equal%20dignity%20and%20value%20of%20all%20human%20life%20%E2%80%93%20and%20its%20automatic%20extension%2C%20a%20commitment%20to%20truth%20and%20justice.%20However%2C%20everything%20about%20the%20way%20Israel%20is%20going%20about%20its%20campaign%20against%20Hamas%20%E2%80%93%20the%20de-humaniwing%20rhetoric%2C%20cutting%20off%20water%2C%20power%2C%20and%20other%20supplies%20to%20Gaza%2C%20indiscriminately%20raining%20down%20bombs%20on%20Gaza%20while%20ignoring%20the%20mounting%20civilian%20cost%20%E2%80%93%20goes%20against%20this%20premise.%20But%20what%20has%20put%20paid%20to%20this%20delusion%20is%20not%20just%20what%20Israel%20is%20doing%20but%20the%20endorsement%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20actions%20by%20the%20apparent%20torchbearers%20of%20liberal%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Russia%20invaded%20Ukraine%2C%20it%20was%20very%20clear%20that%20Putin%20was%20the%20bad%20guy%2C%20the%20entire%20free%20world%20was%20ranged%20against%20Russia%20(with%20some%20abstentions%20but%20certainly%20no%20endorsement).%20But%20now%2C%20not%20only%20is%20the%20world%20leadership%20not%20coming%20together%20as%20one%20to%20demand%20a%20ceasefire%20but%20there%20is%20a%20clampdown%20on%20those%20who%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20152423%2FF80RehHW4AA4TR0.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20152423%2FF80RehHW4AA4TR0.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20152423%2FF80RehHW4AA4TR0-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20152423%2FF80RehHW4AA4TR0-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681050%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20damaged%20school%20building%20in%20Gaza.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40UN_SPExperts%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversations%2C%20people%20have%20raised%20similarities%20between%20US%20actions%20in%20Yemen%2C%20Syria%20%E2%80%93%20and%20of%20course%20the%20invasion%20of%20Iraq%20and%20Afghanistan.%20There%20are%2C%20of%20course%2C%20similarities%20but%20there%20are%20also%20significant%20differences%20in%20the%20nature%20and%20scale%20of%20attack%2C%20which%20sets%20the%20present%20moment%20apart.%20Two%20are%20civil%20wars%20with%20foreign%20involvement%20providing%20support%20to%20one%20or%20the%20other%20faction%20in%20a%20proxy%20war%2C%20here%20an%20entire%20population%20is%20besieged.%20In%20the%20others%2C%20there%20was%20at%20least%20some%20pretense%20of%20wanting%20to%20avoid%20civilian%20casualties.%20One%20example%20of%20this%20was%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FHaska_Meyna_wedding_party_airstrike%5C%22%3EAfghanistan%20wedding%20party%20strike%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%20There%20is%20no%20such%20pretense%20here%2C%20Israel%20with%20the%20backing%20of%20the%20United%20States%20is%20just%20brazening%20it%20out.%20Collective%20punishment%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3Ede%20facto%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Ede%20jure%3C%2Fem%3E%20policy%20of%20this%20attack%20on%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20recurring%20thought%20has%20been%20how%20the%20distinction%20between%20Hamas%20and%20Gaza%20Palestinians%20has%20been%20elided%20to%20justify%20this%20collective%20punishment.%20The%20fact%20that%20Hamas%20is%20the%20elected%20government%20in%20Gaza%20is%20marshaled%20as%20the%20rationale%20for%20the%20collective%20punishment%20of%20Gaza%20Palestinians.%20This%20is%20of%20course%20absurd%20%E2%80%93%20only%20a%20minority%20of%20voters%20actually%20voted%20for%20Hamas%20based%20on%20overall%20turnout%20and%20Hamas%20votes.%20Also%20what%20of%20the%20thousands%20of%20children%20too%20young%20to%20vote%20but%20who%20have%20become%20%E2%80%9Ccollateral%20damage%E2%80%9D%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20destruction%20of%20Gaza%3F%20However%2C%20the%20underlying%20principle%20too%20needs%20to%20be%20called%20out.%20Even%20if%20a%20government%20is%20ostensibly%20very%20popular%2C%20the%20government%20of%20a%20country%20is%20not%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%20because%20representation%20by%20its%20very%20nature%20is%20flawed%20and%20approximate%2C%20not%20precise.%20In%20fact%2C%20very%20often%20even%20supporters%20of%20a%20regime%20may%20disagree%20with%20the%20regime%20on%20individual%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEffacing%20the%20distinction%20between%20the%20leadership%20and%20the%20people%20leaves%20no%20room%20for%20internal%20differences%2C%20democratic%20dissent%2C%20opposition%2C%20and%20individual%20agency.%20Equally%2C%20this%20glosses%20over%20the%20real%20constraints%20of%20people%20in%20being%20able%20to%20represent%20themselves%20given%20the%20limited%20alternatives%20available%20to%20them.%20This%20mistake%20is%20made%20in%20democratic%20countries%20too%2C%20especially%20by%20liberal%20leaders%20and%20intellectuals%20who%20sometimes%20disparage%20voters%20of%20right-wing%20parties%20as%20racist%20or%20bigoted%20without%20introspecting%20on%20their%20own%20inability%20to%20fully%20understand%20and%2For%20represent%20people%20in%20their%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20corollary%20to%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20liberal%20order%20is%20the%20demise%20of%20old%20uncertainties.%20It%20is%20not%20just%20the%20sense%20that%20outright%20war%20is%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past%20or%20more%20generally%20that%20those%20in%20charge%20will%20do%20the%20right%20thing%20%E2%80%93%20but%20that%20it%20is%20no%20longer%20clear%20what%20is%20the%20organising%20principle%20of%20our%20society.%20In%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20the%20global%20leadership%20%E2%80%93%20political%2C%20corporate%2C%20media%2C%20and%20other%20institutions%20%E2%80%93%20has%20shown%20itself%20to%20be%20insular%2C%20incompetent%2C%20and%20more%20interested%20in%20showmanship%20than%20moving%20issues%20forward%20in%20an%20equitable%20way.%20Charlatans%2C%20extremists%2C%20and%20rank%20opportunists%20have%20captured%20the%20discourse.%20All%20of%20this%20has%20contributed%20to%20a%20sense%20of%20chaos%20%E2%80%93%20what%20Yeats%20wrote%20so%20evocatively%20in%20his%20poem%20%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.poetryfoundation.org%2Fpoems%2F43290%2Fthe-second-coming%5C%22%3EThe%20Second%20Coming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThings%20fall%20apart%3B%20the%20centre%20cannot%20hold%3B%20Mere%20anarchy%20is%20loosed%20upon%20the%20world%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frgupta.substack.com%2Fp%2Freflections-on-the-israel-palestine%5C%22%3Epiece%3C%2Fa%3E%20first%20appeared%20on%20the%20author%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frgupta.substack.com%2Fabout%5C%22%3Eblog%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERuchi%20Gupta%20writes%20about%C2%A0democracy%2C%20tech%2C%20publ