on%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ffrom-tiger-3-to-pathaan-and-raazi-the-best-spy%2Fsoldier-movies-you-should-watch-this-festive-season%2Fphotostory%2F105230331.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Shubman%20Gill%20Returned%20To%20Bat%20After%20Going%20Off%20Retired%20Hurt%20-%20Explained%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20cricket%20team%20batter%20Shubman%20Gill%20returned%20to%20bat%20in%20the%20final%20over%20of%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20semifinal%20match%20against%20New%20Zealand%20after%20going%20off%20retired%20hurt.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20was%20dealt%20a%20massive%20blow%20as%20opener%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shubman%20Gill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108578-shubman-gill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20retired%20hurt%20after%20scoring%20a%20brilliant%20half-century%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20Wednesday.%20Gill%20looked%20in%20tremendous%20form%20as%20he%20scored%2079%20off%2065%20deliveries%20before%20he%20started%20suffering%20from%20cramps.%20It%20was%20a%20hot%20and%20sultry%20day%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20during%20the%2023rd%20over%20of%20the%20Indian%20innings%2C%20Gill%20started%20experiencing%20cramps%20and%20had%20to%20lie%20down%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20over.%20The%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20physio%20was%20out%20in%20the%20middle%20and%20after%20couple%20of%20minutes%2C%20Gill%20decided%20to%20leave%20the%20field.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20not%20dismissed%20and%20could%20come%20back%20to%20bat%20after%20a%20stipulated%20time%20period.%C2%A0Here's%20a%20look%20at%20what%20the%20MCC%20rules%20say%20about%20retired%20hurt%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E25.4.1%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20batter%20may%20retire%20at%20any%20time%20during%20his%2Fher%20innings%20when%20the%20ball%20is%20dead.%20The%20umpires%2C%20before%20allowing%20play%20to%20proceed%2C%20shall%20be%20informed%20of%20the%20reason%20for%20a%20batter%20retiring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E25.4.2%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20a%20batter%20retires%20because%20of%20illness%2C%20injury%2C%20or%20any%20other%20unavoidable%20cause%2C%20that%20batter%20is%20entitled%20to%20resume%20his%2Fher%20innings.%20If%20for%20any%20reason%20this%20does%20not%20happen%2C%20that%20batter%20is%20to%20be%20recorded%20as%20%E2%80%98Retired%20-%20not%20out'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20of%20the%20four%20previous%20tournament%20games%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20have%20been%20won%20by%20the%20team%20batting%20first%2C%20with%20the%20exception%20Australia's%20stunning%20defeat%20of%20Afghanistan%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Glenn%20Maxwell%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1423-glenn-maxwell-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGlenn%20Maxwell%3C%2Fa%3E's%20remarkable%20201%20not%20out%20secured%20a%20three-wicket%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20unbeaten%20tournament%20hosts%20India%20and%20New%20Zealand%20were%20unchanged.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20looks%20like%20a%20good%20pitch%2C%20on%20the%20slower%20side%20as%20well%20but%20whatever%20we%20do%2C%20we%20know%20we've%20got%20to%20do%20that%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20opening%20batsman%20Rohit%20at%20the%20toss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Zealand%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kane%20Williamson%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1058-kane-williamson-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKane%20Williamson%3C%2Fa%3E%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20would've%20had%20a%20bat%20first%20as%20well.%20It's%20obviously%20a%20used%20surface%20but%20we'll%20try%20to%20make%20use%20of%20it%20with%20the%20ball%20first%20up%20and%20hopefully%20there's%20some%20dew%20later.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20game%20got%20underway%2C%20India%20cricket