on%20through%20verification%20of%20facts%20before%20publishing%20and%20disseminating%20such%20content%20in%20public%20domain%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20EC%E2%80%99s%20notice%20said%2C%20according%20to%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notice%20also%20claims%20that%20this%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%2C%20in%20October%2C%20lodged%20complaints%20with%20the%20EC%20against%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Assam%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20over%20their%20remarks%20during%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20assembly%20poll%20campaign%2C%20alleging%20that%20they%20violated%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Felections%2Fstory%2Fcongress-files-complaint-against-amit-shah-himanta-biswa-sarma-to-election-commission-poll-code-violations-2453774-2023-10-26%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20in%20its%20complaint%20against%20Shah%2C%20the%20Congress%20told%20the%20EC%20that%20the%20home%20minister%20claimed%20in%20a%20speech%20in%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20Rajnandgaon%20on%20October%2016%20that%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6Bhupesh%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20government%2C%20for%20appeasement%20politics%20and%20vote%20bank%20politics%2C%20lynched%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20son%20Bhuneshwar%20Sahoo%20and%20got%20him%20killed%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sarma%E2%80%99s%20speech%2C%20the%20Congress%20alleged%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20one%20Akbar%20comes%20to%20some%20place%2C%20he%20calls%20100%20Akbars.%20So%2C%20send%20him%20off%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%20otherwise%20the%20land%20of%20Mata%20Kaushalya%20will%20get%20defiled.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20not%20been%20reported%20if%20the%20EC%20has%20show-caused%20the%20two%20BJP%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETransparency%20activist%20Commodore%20Lokesh%20K.%20Batra%20has%20meanwhile%20written%20an%20open%20letter