et-world-cup-2023%2Fvirat-kohlis-special-tribute-to-sachin-tendulkar-after-slamming-historic-century-watch-4576475%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Full%20list%20of%20Virat%20Kohli's%2050%20ODI%20hundreds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700049660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fthumb%2Fmsid-105237215%2Cwidth-1070%2Cheight-580%2Cimgsize-54490%2Cresizemode-75%2Coverlay-toi_sw%2Cpt-32%2Cy_pad-40%2Fphoto.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Fnews%2Ffull-list-of-virat-kohlis-50-odi-hundreds-as-he-breaks-sachin-tendulkars-record%2Farticleshow%2F105237092.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20superstar%20Virat%20Kohli%20hit%20his%20record%2050th%20century%20in%20one-day%20internationals%20at%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20surpassing%20the%20mark%20he%20shared%20with%20countryman%20Sachin%20Tendulkar.%20Kohli%20raised%20his%20arms%20aloft%20then%20sank%20to%20his%20knees%20and%20bowed%20to%20the%20fans%20with%20his%20helmet%20off%20after%20reaching%20three%20figures%20in%20the%20semifinal%20match%20against%20New%20Zealand%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20stadium.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22White%20AI-generated%20faces%20are%20more%20convincing%20than%20photographs%20of%20real%20humans%2C%20study%20finds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DALL-E%202%20AI-generated%20image%20of%20a%20young%20woman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6554a3ac4ca513d824299fdf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAI-generated%20image%20of%20a%20young%20woman.%3Cp%3EOpen%20AI%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAI-generated%20white%20faces%20are%C2%A0more%20convincing%20than%20photographs%20of%20real%20humans%2C%20a%20study%20has%20found.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20the%20results%20were%20not%20the%20same%20for%20AI%20images%20of%20people%20of%20color.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20may%20be%20because%20most%20AI%20models%20are%20disproportionately%20trained%20on%20white%20faces%2C%20the%20study%20found.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20AI-generated%20faces%20are%20already%20indistinguishable%20from%20photographs%20of%20real%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2C%20that's%20what%20a%20new%20study%20published%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdx.doi.org%2F10.1177%2F09567976231207095%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPsychological%20Science%3C%2Fa%3E%20journal%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%2C%20which%20was%20conducted%20by%20researchers%20from%20universities%20in%20Canada%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20London%2C%20carried%20out%20two%20experiments%20that%20tested%20people's%20ability%20to%20identify%20AI-created%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%2C%20where%20124%20participants%20were%20asked%20to%20judge%20whether%20a%20face%20was%20AI-generated%20or%20real%2C%20the%20researchers%20found%20that%20caucasian%20AI%20faces%20were%20judged%20as%20human%20more%20often%20than%20photographs%20of%20real%20human%20faces.%20Participants%20were%20also%20asked%20to%20rate%20their%20confidence%20in%20their%20answers%20on%20a%20100-point%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20found%20that%2066%25%20of%20AI%20images%20of%20white%20faces%20were%20rated%20as%20human%2C%20while%2051%25%20of%20real%20images%20were%20identified%20as%20such%2C%20the%20study%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRemarkably%2C%20white%20AI%20faces%20can%20convincingly%20pass%20as%20more%20real%20than%20human%20faces%20%E2%80%94%20and%20people%20do%20not%20realize%20they%20are%20being%20fooled%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20researchers%20said%20in%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20results%20were%20different%20for%20pictures%20of%20people%20of%20color.%20The%20report%20noted%20that%20this%20may%20be%20because%20most%20AI%20models%20were%20disproportionately%20trained%20on%20white%20faces%2C%20which%20made%20them%20appear%20%26quot%3Bespecially%20realistic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20study's%20authors%2C%20Zak%20Witkower%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2023%2Fnov%2F13%2Fwhite-faces-generated-by-ai-are-more-convincing-than-photos-finds-survey%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20this%20meant%20AI%20was%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20to%20produce%20more%20realistic%20situations%20for%20white%20faces%20than%20other%20race%20faces.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20warned%20that%20if%20the%20issues%20remained%20unaddressed%2C%20such%20bias%20could%20have%20real-world%20consequences%2C%20ranging%20from%20%26quot%3Binfluencing%20elections%20to%20finding%20missing%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20several%20examples%20of%20instances%20of%20basis%20found%20in%20the%20training%20data%20and%20output%20of%20popular%20AI%20models%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fchatgpt-is-like-many-other-ai-models-rife-with-bias-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearly%20versions%20of%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20have%20warned%20for%20some%20time%20that%20the%20widespread%20adoption%20of%20AI%20models%20could%20cause%20trouble%20for%20marginalized%20groups%20if%20the%20issues%20are%20not%20properly%20addressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-faces-indistinguishable-from-real-humans-study-finds-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700049500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6554a3ef22cf74a5739786b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-faces-indistinguis