overnment%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leaders%20in%20Telangana%20have%20been%20waxing%20eloquent%20that%20the%20five%20guarantees%20promised%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Karnataka%20were%20delivered%20within%20the%20100-day%20deadline%2C%20but%20the%20BRS%20and%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20have%20been%20refuting%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20claim.%20The%20BRS%20has%20been%20specifically%20targeting%20Congress%20for%20its%20alleged%20inability%20to%20provide%2024-hour%20power%20supply%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20five%20guarantees%20promised%20by%20the%20Congress%20did%20not%20reach%20the%20people%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20party%20MP%20Manish%20Tewari%2C%20who%20was%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20said%20it%20was%20because%20of%20the%20obstacles%20set%20up%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20victory%20boosted%20the%20sagging%20morale%20of%20the%20Congress%20cadre%20and%20supporters%20in%20Telangana%20going%20by%20huge%20turnout%20at%20election%20rallies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20K.%20Nageshwar%2C%20who%20is%20a%20former%20member%20of%20the%20legislative%20council%2C%20says%20the%20Karnataka%20victory%20has%20helped%20the%20Congress%20to%20change%20the%20negative%20perception%20people%20had%20of%20the%20party%20in%20Telangana%20that%20days%20of%20the%20party%20were%20over%20in%20the%20state.%20Otherwise%2C%20consecutive%20defeats%20suffered%20by%20Congress%20in%20byelections%20to%20the%20Assembly%20created%20a%20perception%20in%20the%20public%20mind%20that%20the%20party%20was%20no%20longer%20a%20force.%20Worse%20still%2C%20it%20won%20only%20two%20out%20of%20150%20divisions%20in%20the%20Greater%20Hyderabad%20Municipal%20Corporation%20elections.%20But%2C%20there%20is%20now%20a%20feeling%20that%20Congress%20has%20revived%2C%20Nageshwar%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20professor%20and%20president%20of%20Telangana%20Jana%20Samiti%20M.%20Kodandaram%20echoes%20Nageshwar%E2%80%99s%20observation%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Telangana%20had%20lost%20confidence%20in%20Congress%20prior%20to%20the%20Karnataka%20elections.%20Now%2C%20they%20see%20Congress%20as%20the%20only%20alternative%20to%20ruling%20BRS.%20They%20want%20an%20elected%20government%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20Karnataka.%20The%20BJP%2C%20which%20was%20dethroned%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20stands%20no%20chance%20in%20the%20present%20scenario%20in%20Telangana%2C%20says%20Kodandaram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20has%20been%20making%20a%20frontal%20attack%20against%20Congress%20primarily%20on%20two%20counts%20that%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20deliver%20on%20its%20five%20guarantees%20as%20well%20as%20the%20apparent%20power%20outages%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15170243%2FF-9URpGboAADbuz.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15170243%2FF-9URpGboAADbuz.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15170243%2FF-9URpGboAADbuz-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15170243%2FF-9URpGboAADbuz-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684916%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKarnataka%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20D.K.%20Shivakumar.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40DKShivakumar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%E2%80%99%20friendly%20party%20in%20Karnataka%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20has%20joined%20the%20row%20to%20mount%20criticism%20against%20Congress.%20Its%20leader%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20H.%20D.%20Kumaraswamy%20has%20appealed%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Telangana%20not%20to%20be%20carried%20away%20by%20Congress%20guarantees%20as%20they%20were%20an%20eyewash%20in%20his%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20ridiculed%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20D.K.%20Shivakumar%20for%20campaigning%20on%20behalf%20of%20Congress%20in%20%E2%80%9Cpower%20surplus%E2%80%9D%20Telangana%20while%20the%20supply%20was%20a%20meagre%20two%20hours%20out%20of%20the%20promised%20five%20hours%20for%20agriculture%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20Shivakumar%20urged%20people%20during%20their%20campaign%20in%20Telangana%20a%20few%20days%20ago%20to%20visit%20Karnataka%20to%20see%20for%20themselves%20the%20development%20model%20and%20five-hour%20power%20supply%20in%20the%20state%20under%20the%20new%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20the%20offer%20to%20the%20next%20level%20was%20Telangana%20Congress%20chief%20A.%20Revanth%20Reddy%20who%20promised%20to%20facilitate%20the%20visit%20by%20arranging%20buses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20come%20up%20with%20six%20guarantees%20in%20Telangana%20but%20they%20became%20a%20tool%20for%20BRS%20to%20launch%20the%20attack%20against%20the%20rival%20party.%20In%20tune%20with%20Kumaraswamy%E2%80%99s%20observation%2C%20BRS%20working%20president%20K.%20T.%20Rama%20Rao%20and%20his%20Cabinet%20colleague%20T.%20Harish%20Rao%20also%20said%20the%20guarantees%20were%20given%20a%20go-by%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intervention%20of%20Kumaraswamy%20invited%20criticism%20from%20the%20Congress%20as%20it%20alleged%20the%20role%20of%20BRS%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevanth%20Reddy%20claimed%20that%20Harish%20Rao%20brought%20pressure%20on%20newspapers%20and%20news%20channels%20to%20play%20up%20Kumaraswamy%E2%80%99s%20media%20conference%20held%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Reddy%2C%20it%20was%20a%20deliberate%20attempt%20to%20divert%20the%20attention%20of%20people%20from%20the%20Congress%20campaign%2C%20which%20has%20been%20highlighting%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfailures%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20BRS%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20has%20repeatedly%20raised%20the%20critical%20power%20situation%20since%20the%20Congress%20assumed%20power%20in%20Karnataka%20to%20show%20the%20party%20in%20a%20poor%20light%20ahead%20of%20elections%20in%20Telangana.%20Chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20maintained%20that%20Congress%20could%20not%20win%20Telangana%20as%20conditions%20in%20the%20two%20states%20differed%20vastly.%20He%20pointed%20out%20the%20poor%20power%20position%20in%20Karnataka%20as%20against%2024-hour%20quality%20supply%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20farmers%20from%20Karnataka%20staged%20a%20demonstration%20expressing%20their%20ire%20against%20Congress%20a%20few%20days%20ago%20at%20Kodangal%20where%20Revanth%20Reddy%20is%20seeking%20election.%20Another%20bigger%20show%20by%20them%20is%20scheduled%20on%20November%2022%20at%20Hyderabad%20but%20the%20Election%20Commission%20has%20not%20yet%20given%20permission.%20The%20Congress%20claimed%20that%20the%20BRS%20was%20behind%20both%20the%20events%20though%20the%20permission%20on%20November%2022%20was%20sought%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Karnataka%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20outcry%20against%20guarantees%20and%20power%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20there%20were%20also%20behind%20the%20scene%20political%20developments%20in%20Congress%20which%20reinforced%20the%20position%20of%20party%20leadership%20from%20Karnataka%20as%20a%20strong%C2%A0%20player%20in%20the%20November%2030%20elections%20in%20Telangana.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20Kumaraswamy%E2%80%99s%20remark%20that%20the%20the%20party%20was%20sending%20crores%20of%20rupees%20from%20Karnataka%20to%20fund%20election%20in%20Telangana%20assumed%20significance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20Revanth%20Reddy%20called%20on%20Shivakumar%20in%20Bengaluru%20twice%2C%20on%20one%20occasion%20reportedly%20to%20request%20him%20to%20camp%20in%20Telangana%20till%20the%20elections%20and%20another%20to%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20a%20BRS%20leader%20Tummala%20Nageswara%20Rao%20to%20join%20the%20Congress%20and%20contest%20from%20Khammam.%20As%20a%20poll%20strategist%2C%20Shivakumar%20was%20tasked%20with%20dissidence%20management%20by%20the%20Congress%20high%20command%20in%20the%20last%20Assembly%20elections%20of%20Telangana.%20He%20was%20among%2060-odd%20leaders%20from%20Karnataka%20who%20were%20roped%20in%20for%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYSR%20Telangana%20president%20Sharmila%20Reddy%20also%20met%20him%20thrice%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months%20to%20discuss%20her%20association%20with%20Congress.%20She%20may%20be%20offered%20membership%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20from%20Karnataka%20as%20the%20Congress%20candidate%2C%20according%20to%20the%20political%20grapevine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700048294000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15165404%2FThe-Wire-81.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-polls-the-performance-of-congress-govt-in-karnataka-has-emerged-as-a-key-talking-point%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Even%20though%20victory%20in%20Karnataka%20has%20boosted%20the%20morale%20of%20Congress%20cadres%20in%20Telangana%2C%20the%20alleged%20failures%20of%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%20is%20being%20used%20by%20the%20ruling%20BRS%20to%20attack%20the%20rival%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-polls-the-performance-of-congress-govt-in-karnataka-has-emerged-as-a-key-talking-point%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Virat%20surpasses%20Sachin%20with%20record-breaking%2050th%20ODI%20ton%22%2C%22content