20extending%20credit%20terms%20up%20to%2045%20days%20to%20retailers%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20This%20is%20due%20to%20the%20doubling%20of%20inventory%20days%2C%20as%20there%E2%80%99s%20stress%20in%20the%20rate%20at%20which%20consumers%20are%20purchasing%20goods%2C%20distributors%20told%20the%20business%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20major%20brands%20are%20experiencing%20a%20doubling%20of%20inventory%20days%2C%20with%20some%20food%20sector%20companies%20seeing%20up%20to%2060%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFestival%20season%20demand%20did%20not%20offer%20any%20respite%20this%20year%2C%20and%20the%20summer%20wedding%20season%20remained%20weak%2C%20causing%20a%20build-up%20in%20inventory%20for%20the%20past%20few%20months.%20One%20has%20to%20see%20how%20demand%20plays%20out%20after%20the%20rabi%20season%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20distributor%20based%20in%20the%20east%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20distributor%20mentioned%20that%2C%20although%20he%20did%20not%20extend%20credit%20to%20retailers%2C%20he%20opted%20to%20sell%20lower%20stocks%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%2020%25%20drop%20in%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRetailers%20have%20been%20asking%20for%20higher%20credit%20days%2C%20but%20I%20decided%20to%20sell%20lower%20stock%20instead%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20same%20in%20all%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20North%20India%2C%20inventory%20days%20have%20more%20than%20doubled%20to%20around%2040%20days%2C%20which%20is%20typically%2015%20days%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20distributor%20in%20North%20India%20told%20the%20newspaper%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20festival%20season%2C%20demand%20has%20been%20down%20by%2030-35%25%20compared%20to%20the%20average%20Diwali%20offtake%20that%20we%20witness.%20Gift%20packs%2C%20which%20see%20high%20demand%20during%20this%20time%2C%20have%20not%20sold%20well%2C%20nor%20have%20beverages%20or%20namkeens%20(salty%20snacks)%2C%20which%20typically%20witness%20a%20strong%20pick-up%20during%20this%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECredit%20to%20retailers%20for%20fast-moving%20stock-keeping%20units%20is%20at%2025%E2%80%9326%20days.%20This%20typically%20means%20retailers%20clear%20payments%20to%20distributors%20in%20seven%20to%20eight%20days.%20For%20slow-moving%20items%2C%20credit%20days%20have%20increased%20to%2035-40%20days%20from%2015-20%20days%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20inventory%20pile-up%20amid%20lack%20of%20demand%20is%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20reports%20released%20by%20NIQ%20(formerly%20known%20as%20NielsenIQ)%20and%20Bizom%2C%20which%20reported%20a%20growth%20in%20the%20FMCG%20industry%2C%20in%20both%20rural%20and%20urban%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%20noted%20this%20observation%2C%20citing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Ffmcg-growth-up-in-sep-qtr-signs-of-rural-recovery-seen-11699379228097.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DRural%2520markets%2520reported%2520a%25206.4%2Cperiod%252C%2520NIQ%2520said%2520on%2520Tuesday.%5C%22%3ENIQ%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20said%20that%20rural%20markets%20showed%20%E2%80%9Csigns%20of%20recovery%E2%80%9D%2C%20with%20consumption%20picking%20up%20in%20the%20September%20quarter%20compared%20to%20the%20year-ago%20period%2C%20while%20urban%20markets%20maintained%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstable%20rate%20of%20consumption%20growth%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsumer%20goods%20sales%20(without%20considering%20branded%20commodities)%20in%20urban%20areas%20grew%20by%201.6%25%2C%20while%20rural%20areas%20witnessed%20a%20substantial%20increase%20of%2010.2%25%2C%20Bizom%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20slowdown%20in%20the%20FMCG%20sector%20has%20been%20confirmed%20by%20the%20big%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CObviously%20there%20is%20a%20slowdown%20as%20far%20as%20FMCG%20is%20concerned.%20We%20are%20seeing%20a%20clear%20slowdown%20in%20rural.%20Despite%20us%20continuing%20to%20get%20deeper%20into%20rural%20areas%2C%20getting%20into%20more%20villages%2C%20etc.%2C%20we%20have%20started%20to%20see%20the%20rural%20economy%20to%20splutter%20a%20bit.%20However%2C%20these%20are%20macro%20issues%20which%20companies%20like%20us%20cannot%20sort%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20Varun%20Berry%2C%20executive%20vice-chairman%20and%20managing%20director%2C%20Britannia%20Industries%20Ltd%2C%20said%20during%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20post%20earnings%20call%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Frural-demand-slows-down-for-fmcg-11699029760068.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarico%20said%20that%20while%20urban%20sentiment%20improved%20sequentially%2C%20instances%20of%20higher%20food%20inflation%20and%20uneven%20rainfall%20distribution%20led%20to%20a%20slower-than-expected%20pace%20of%20recovery%20in%20rural%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaugata%20Gupta%2C%20Marico%20MD%20and%20CEO%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20rural%20demand%20continues%20to%20lag%20urban.%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20said%20that%2C%20when%20we%20look%20at%20the%20overall%20volume%20growth%2C%20demand%20is%20not%20the%20only%20factor.%20There%20are%20other%20things%20that%20have%20happened.%20There%20has%20been%20some%20inflation%20and%20some%20down%20trading%20and%20in%20some%20of%20our%20categories%2C%20that%20down%20trading%20can%20be%20to%20smaller%20brands%2C%20or%20to%20unbranded%20goods%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20the%20business%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindustan%20Unilever%20and%20Dabur%20also%20said%20that%20the%20rural%20markets%20are%20lagging%20urban%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20PTI%20reported%20a%20decline%20in%20rural%20consumption%20due%20to%20persistent%20food%20inflation%20and%20uneven%20rains%20in%20some%20regions.%20It%20reported%20that%20the%20FMCG%20industry%20has%20witnessed%20a%20challenging%20September%20quarter%20amid%20subdued%20consumer%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Feconomy%2Frural-demand-revival-what-new-data-tells-us-11698085155203.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20FY24%2C%20some%20of%20these%20companies%20have%20done%20well%2C%20while%20others%20have%20not.%20This%20has%20raised%20doubts%20about%20revival%20in%20rural%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20a%20third%20of%20consumer%20goods%20companies%E2%80%99%20revenues%20are%20attributed%20to%20rural%20demand%2C%20reflecting%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20rural%20economy.%20And%20a%20majority%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population%20lives%20in%20rural%20areas.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20rural%20economy%E2%80%99s%20growth%20and%20development%20are%20crucial%20to%20the%20overall%20growth%20and%20inclusive%20development%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700048197000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15171005%2F1024px-Supermarket_full_of_goods.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fmore-inventory-days-for-consumer-goods-as-low-demand-causes-supply-chain-congestion%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20distributors%20are%20extending%20credit%20terms%20up%20to%2045%20days%20to%20retailers%2C%20'Business%20Standard'%20reported.%20This%20is%20due%20to%20the%20doubling%20of%20inventory%20days%2C%20as%20there's%20stress%20in%20the%20rate%20at%20which%20consumers%20are%20purchasing%20goods%2C%20distributors%20told%20the%20business%20daily.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fmore-inventory-days-for-consumer-goods-as-low-demand-causes-supply-chain-congestion%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sunny%20Deol-Rahul%20Rawail%20to%20talk%20at%20IFFI%202023%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700048096000%2C%22vis