EIs%20now%20a%20good%20time%20to%20buy%20the%20Meta%20Quest%202%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou're%20much%20more%20likely%20to%20find%20a%20Meta%20(aka%20Oculus)%20Quest%202%20on%20sale%20during%20Black%20Friday%20than%20the%20newer%20model.%20We've%20spotted%20rare%20discounts%20early%20at%20retailers%20like%20Walmart%20that%20take%20as%20much%20as%20%2450%20off%20the%20%24300%20going%20price.%20It's%20not%20quite%20as%20nice%20as%20the%20Quest%203.%20Still%2C%20Meta%20has%20committed%20to%20continued%20support%20for%20the%20Quest%202%2C%20previously%20noting%20that%20those%20holding%20onto%20the%20older%20headset%20will%20continue%20to%20enjoy%20nearly%20all%20of%20the%20VR%20games%20launching%20in%20the%20Meta%20Store%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Csection%20data-component-type%3D%5C%22post-author%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fblack-friday-meta-quest-3-and-oculus-quest-2-deals-and-bundles%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700047063000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654ab44b3cc84b4dfafe37d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fblack-friday-meta-quest-3-and-oculus-quest-2-deals-and-bundles%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Black%20Friday%20Meta%20Quest%20deals%20should%20make%20this%20VR%20headset%20more%20affordable%20than%20ever.%20We're%20rounding%20up%20all%20the%20best%20Quest%202%20deals%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20big%20sale%20weekend.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22qkennemer%40insider.com%20(Quentyn%20Kennemer)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fblack-friday-meta-quest-3-and-oculus-quest-2-deals-and-bundles%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Retailers%20and%20delivery%20apps%20must%20act%20on%20e-bike%20safety%2C%20NY%20officials%20say%2C%20after%203%20people%20died%20in%20a%20house%20fire%20linked%20with%20a%20scooter%20battery%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221778%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20GrubHub%20rider%20in%20New%20York%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6554a5ef4ca513d82429a084%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20GrubHub%20rider%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3Cp%3ESeth%20Wenig%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENew%20York%20City%20officials%20say%20retailers%20and%20food%20delivery%20apps%20must%20act%20on%20unsafe%20e-bike%20batteries.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20call%20comes%20after%20a%20fire%20blamed%20on%20an%20e-scooter's%20lithium%20ion%20battery%20killed%20three%20people.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20have%20been%20hundreds%20of%20fires%20linked%20to%20lithium%20ion%20batteries%20in%20e-bikes%20and%20scooters%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENEW%20YORK%20(AP)%20%E2%80%94%20New%20York%20City%20officials%20say%20retailers%20and%20food%20delivery%20companies%20must%20do%20more%20to%20halt%20the%20proliferation%20of%20unsafe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-bikes-popularity-sustainability-evs-2023-4%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3Ee-bike%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20e-scooter%20batteries%2C%20after%20a%20fire%20blamed%20on%20an%20electric%20scooter's%20lithium%20ion%20battery%20killed%20three%20people%20over%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20blood%20on%20the%20hands%20of%20this%20private%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20Fire%20Commissioner%20Laura%20Kavanagh%20said%20at%20a%20news%20conference%20Monday%20in%20front%20of%20the%20charred%20remains%20of%20the%20Brooklyn%20house%20where%20the%20blaze%20on%20Sunday%20killed%20Albertha%20West%2C%2081%2C%20her%20son%20Michael%20West%2C%2058%2C%20and%20her%20grandson%20Jamiyl%20West%2C%2033.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFire%20officials%20said%20the%20fire%20broke%20out%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20of%20the%20building.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20extensively%20damaged%2C%26quot%3B%20Kavanagh%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20battery%20that%20sparked%20the%20fire%20was%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bscooter%20of%20some%20kind.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20has%20seen%20hundreds%20of%20fires%20linked%20to%20the%20lithium%20ion%20batteries%20that%20power%20electric%20bikes%20and%20scooters%20in%20recent%20years.%20City%20officials%20have%20blamed%20off-market%20batteries%20and%20chargers%20that%20don't%20meet%20safety%20standards%20for%20many%20of%20the%20fires%2C%20and%20they%20have%20lobbied%20the%20federal%20government%20to%20strengthen%20regulations%20governing%20the%20sale%20of%20e-bikes%20and%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Kavanagh%20said%20companies%20also%20have%20a%20role%20to%20play%20too%3A%20%26quot%3BRetailers%20like%20Amazon%20and%20Walmart%20need%20to%20stop%20selling%20devices%20that%20are%20not%20safety%20certified%20by%20a%20national%20testing%20laboratory%2C%20and%20food%20service%20apps%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-does-grubhub-work%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3EGrubhub%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-uber-eats%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3EUber%20Eats%3C%2Fa%3E%20need%20to%20do%20more%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20their%20workers%20who%20depend%20on%20these%20bikes%20to%20make%20a%20living.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECity%20officials%20haven't%20said%20whether%20the%20battery%20that%20caused%20Sunday's%20fire%20came%20from%20a%20vehicle%20used%20to%20make%20deliveries%20for%20one%20of%20the%20food%20service%20apps%2C%20and%20they%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20Tuesday%20email%20seeking%20further%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%26quot%3BSpeed%20is%20rewarded%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETens%20of%20thousands%20of%20the%20city's%20food%20delivery%20workers%20rely%20on%20e-bikes%20to%20get%20dinner%20to%20customers%20quickly%2C%20and%20Deputy%20Mayor%20for%20Operations%20Meera%20Joshi%20singled%20out%20the%20delivery%20industry%20during%20remarks%20at%20a%20City%20Hall%20news%20conference%20Tuesday%2C%20noting%20that%20time%20is%20money%20for%20delivery%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20paid%20to%20deliver%20and%20speed%20is%20rewarded%2C%26quot%3B%20Joshi%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20speed%20means%20oftentimes%20they%20take%20risky%20moves%20like%20using%20uncertified%20batteries%20and%20bikes%20and%20chargers%2C%20or%20changing%20the%20mechanics%20of%20the%20bike%20so%20that%20they%20go%20faster%20so%20that%20they%20can%20make%20more%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoshi%20said%20New%20Yorkers%20should%20ask%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20is%20the%20role%20of%20the%20apps%20in%20this%3F%20What%20is%20their%20responsibility%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20workers%20that%20they%20profit%20from%20have%20safe%20equipment%20without%20having%20to%20pay%20for%20it%20themselves%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJosh%20Gold%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Uber%2C%20said%20online%20retailers%20should%20stop%20selling%20devices%20that%20haven't%20been%20certified%20by%20UL%2C%20a%20company%20that%20conducts%20product%20safety%20testing%20on%20electronics.%20%26quot%3BIn%20March%2C%20Uber%20called%20for%20the%20City%20to%20implement%20a%20small%20fee%20on%20all%20food%20deliveries%20to%20help%20transition%20this%20industry%20to%20UL-certified%20bikes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrubhub%20spokesperson%20Patrick%20Burke%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe've%20repeatedly%20called%20on%20New%20York%20City%20and%20the%20US%20Congress%20to%20provide%20safe%20charging%20hubs%20for%20delivery%20partners%2C%20to%20establish%20a%20product%20safety%20standard%20for%20rechargeable%20lithium-ion%20batteries%2C%20and%20to%20address%20concerns%20related%20to%20illegal%2C%20unregulated%20charging%20devices%20widely%20available%20for%20purchase%20through%20online%20retailers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart%20officials%20said%20in%20a%20statement%3A%20%26quot%3BWalmart%20has%20zero%20tolerance%20for%20fraudulent%20sellers%20or%20the%20sale%20of%20products%20with%20false%20claims.%20Like%20our%20customers%2C%20we%20expect%20sellers%20and%20suppliers%20to%20provide%20accurate%20and%20honest%20descriptions%20about%20their%20products.%20When%20we%20identify%20a%20false%20claim%2C%20we%20take%20action%20to%20protect%20our%20customers%20and%20maintain%20their%20trust.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20said%20in%20a%20statement%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20strive%20to%20ensure%20all%20products%20offered%20in%20our%20store%20to%20comply%20with%20applicable%20laws%2C%20regulations%20and%20Amazon%20policies%E2%80%94including%20NYC%20Local%20Law%2039.%20We%20ensure%20our%20selection%20meets%20industry-accepted%20standards%2C%20and%20we%20develop%20innovative%20tools%20to%20prevent%20the%20sale%20of%20unsafe%20products.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-bikes-scooters-retailers-delivery-apps-action-safety-fire-ny-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700046985000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6554a5ef4ca513d82429a084%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-bikes-scooters-retailers-delivery-apps-action-safety-fire-ny-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22New%20York%20City%20officials%20linked%20substandard%20batteries%20and%20chargers%20for%20electric%20bikes%20and%20scooters%20with%20some%20of%20the%20hundreds%20of%20fires%20in%20recent%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Insider%20Inc.)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-bikes-scooters-retailers-delivery-apps-action-safety-fire-ny-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22am