2210%5C%22%3EThe%20Israeli%20military's%20overnight%20entry%20into%20Gaza%20City's%20Al-Shifa%20hospital%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bflagrant%20violation%20of%20international%20law%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20Palestinian%20foreign%20ministry%20said%2C%20demanding%20%26quot%3Burgent%20international%20intervention%20to%20protect%20the%20civilians%20there%26quot%3B.%20The%20UN%20estimates%20there%20are%20at%20least%202%2C300%20patients%2C%20staff%20and%20displaced%20civilians%20inside%20the%20facility.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fpalestinian-authority-slams-israel-hospital-raid-as-violation-of-international-law%2Farticleshow%2F105235815.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fpalestinian-authority-slams-israel-hospital-raid-as-violation-of-international-law%2Famp_articleshow%2F105235815.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fpalestinian-authority-slams-israel-hospital-raid-as-violation-of-international-law%2Famp_articleshow%2F105235815.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telegram%2C%20Paytm%20Face%20Criminal%20Case%20Over%20Child%20Sex%20Abuse%20Content%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHyderabad-based%20child%20rights%20activist%20Sunitha%20Krishnan%20has%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20messaging%20app%20Telegram%20and%20digital%20payment%20apps%20PhonePe%20and%20Paytm%20for%20allegedly%20abetting%20in%20the%20sale%20of%20child%20sex%20abuse%20material%2C%20or%20CSAM%2C%20and%20building%20an%20ecosystem%20that%20allows%20sexual%20exploitation%20of%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Krishnan%20called%20on%20the%20popular%20digital%20platforms%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20the%20sale%20of%20CSAM%20via%20their%20networks%2C%20and%20demanded%20to%20know%20what%20protocols%20have%20been%20put%20in%20place%20to%20prevent%20distribution%20and%20sale%20of%20sexually%20explicit%20material%20involving%20children%2C%20including%20adult%20photography.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Krishnan%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20tech%20platforms%20for%20%26quot%3Bmindfully%20(and)%20wilfully%26quot%3B%20aiding%20in%20the%20spread%20of%20CSAM%20and%20has%20demanded%20they%20%26quot%3Bbe%20aware%20where%20(and%20how)%20they%20are%20earning%20their%20money%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20Paytm%2C%20PhonePe%2C%20nor%20Telegram%2C%20have%20responded%2C%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelegram%20is%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20popular%20IM%2C%20or%20instant%20messaging%2C%20apps%20with%20700%20million%20users%20worldwide%3B%20India%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20Russia%20are%20its%20biggest%20markets.%20The%20app%20offers%20extensive%20security%20features%2C%20including%20end-to-end%20encryption%2C%20private%20channels%20and%20self-destructing%20messages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Krishnan%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Prajwala%20-%20a%20NGO%20that%20combats%20sex%20trafficking%20-%20said%20she%20had%20been%20following%20a%20casual%20lead%20when%20she%20was%20shocked%20at%20how%20easy%20it%20was%20to%20find%20CSAM%20online.%20She%20was%20also%20shocked%20by%20the%20large%20number%20of%20people%20illegally%20buying%20and%20selling%20videos%20of%20sex%20acts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20these%20were%20performed%2C%20she%20suspects%2C%20by%20minors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Krishnan%2C%20awarded%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20in%202016%2C%20said%20she%20chose%20to%20file%20the%20complaint%20on%20Tuesday%20because%20it%20was%20Children's%20Day%2C%20and%20because%20she%20wanted%20to%20red-flag%20dangers%20they%20face%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20Investigation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20had%20been%20told%20of%20some%20Telegram%20accounts%20circulating%20CSAM.%20She%20downloaded%20the%20app%20at%20her%20office%20in%20Hyderabad%20and%20posed%20as%20a%20buyer.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20verification%20(to%20establish%20the%20name)%20and%20I%20could%20name%20myself%20under%20a%20pseudonym%2C%20which%20I%20chose%20as%20Vashisht%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Krishnan%20explained%20the%20Telegram%20app%20has%20a%20search%20bar%20on%20the%20home%20page%20that%20lets%20you%20find%20groups%2Fcontent%2Fpeople%20with%20certain%20keywords%20-%20much%20like%20Google.%20%26quot%3BI%20came%20across%20a%20group%20called%20'Girls%20and%20Boys%20Chatting'.%20...%20on%20entering%20the%20group%2C%20which%20had%2031%2C000%20members%2C%20I%20found%20a%20stream%20of%20messages%20(selling)%20different%20categories%20of%20explicit%20material%2C%20including%20CSAM.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20encryption%20features%20sometimes%20don't%20allow%20screenshots.%20The%20self-destruct%20feature%20of%20Telegram%20gives%20operators%20anonymity%20and%20safety%20from%20being%20tracked%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThese%20private%20channels%20allow%20the%20admin%20to%20admit%20and%20remove%20members%20and%20not%20be%20visible%20in%20general%20search%20results.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20established%20contact%20with%20three%20sellers%20for%20CSAM%2C%20and%20made%20payments%20via%20the%20Paytm%20or%20PhonePe%20app%20in%20each%20case.%20From%20one%20seller%20she%20found%20CSAM%20for%20Rs%2050%20and%20purchased%20more%20links%20after%20negotiating%20the%20amount%20from%20Rs%20400%20to%20Rs%20150.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20asked%20why%20there%20was%20a%20delay%20after%20payment%2C%20the%20seller%20said%20he%20had%20gone%20for%20tuitions.%20That%20is%20when%20I%20realised%20this%20is%20a%20minor%20I%20am%20dealing%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CSAM%20delivered%20contained%20scenes%20of%20oral%20sex%20and%20intercourse%20with%20children%2C%20solo%20streaming%20of%20children%20between%20three%20and%2012%20years%20of%20age%20as%20well%20as%20adult%20pornography.%20%26quot%3BIt%20also%20contained%20videos%20of%20(alleged)%20gang-rape%20(with)%20and%20molesters%20seeming%20to%20be%20from%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Rs%20100%20(via%20PhonePe%20to%20the%20second)%2C%20she%20was%20given%20access%20to%20six%20private%20channels%20containing%20explicit%20material.%20From%20a%20third%2C%20on%20payment%20of%20Rs%2050%20(also%20PhonePe)%2C%20she%20got%20access%20to%20CSAM%20links%2C%20including%20adults%20participating%20in%20intercourse%20with%20children%20and%20self-streaming%20by%20underage%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Krishnan%20said%20she%20came%20across%20groups%20with%20as%20many%20as%2040%2C000%20members%3B%20528%20were%20online%20at%20one%20time.%20The%20seller%20on%20one%20group%20offered%20access%20to%20his%20private%20channel%20through%20links%20upon%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20payment%2C%20the%20seller%20gave%20her%20access%20to%20a%20channel%20called%20'desi%20videos'%20that%20contained%20adult%20pornography.%20After%20she%20complained%2C%20he%20gave%20her%20access%20to%20a%20channel%20named%20'Heart%204'.%20She%20paid%20Rs%2080%20more%20and%20got%20access%20to%20a%20'Heart2'%20channel%20that%20contained%20more%20CSAM%2C%20including%20pictures%20of%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%26quot%3BNo%20Warning%20From%20Telegram%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThrough%20this%20entire%20exercise%2C%20not%20a%20single%20pop-up%20appeared%20on%20Telegram%2C%20warning%20that%20dissemination%20of%20child%20sexually%20abusive%20material%20is%20a%20criminal%20offence%20and%20not%20reporting%20the%20same%20may%20attract%20POCSO%20Act%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20arguing%20Telegram%20is%20therefore%20facilitating%20sale%20and%20purchase%20of%20CSAM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20not%20verifying%20identities%2C%20she%20added%2C%20Telegram%20is%20allowing%20those%20engaged%20in%20distribution%20to%20conceal%20their%20names.%20And%20Telegram's%20end-to-end%20encryption%20allows%20transactions%20to%20purchase%20such%20material.%20Encryption%20settings%20allow%20prevention%20of%20screenshots%2C%20copying%20of%20links%20and%20collection%20of%20any%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPhonePe%20and%20Paytm%20have%20been%20instrumental%20in%20providing%20QR%20access%20to%20such%20sellers%20to%20distribute%20such%20material%20at%20extremely%20low%20costs%20with%20ease%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20Next%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Krishnan%20has%20complained%20to%20Telangana%20DGP%20Anjani%20Kumar%20and%20intends%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCirculation%20of%20such%20sexually%20exploitative%20content%20of%20children%20threatens%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20all%20children%20and%20are%20grievous%20criminal%20offenses.%20Demand%20for%20CSAM%20will%20accelerate%20child%20trafficking%20for%20sexual%20exploitation.%20It%20is%20not%20enough%20to%20take%20action%20against%20the%20few%20players%20I%20randomly%20came%20across.%20Immediate%20and%20urgent%20action%20should%20be%20taken%20against%20Telegram%2C%20PhonePe%20and%20Paytm%20so%20as%20to%20prevent%20any%20more%20children%20being%20sexually%20exploited...%26quot%3B%20she%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700046720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-04%2Fchild-abuse-istock-650_650x400_51460717509.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsunitha-krishnan-child-sex-abuse-material-telegram-paytm-phonepe-activists-case-against-telegram-paytm-for-enabling-child-sex-abuse-content-4575853%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hyderabad-based%20child%20rights%20activist%20Sunitha%20Krishnan%20has%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20messaging%20app%20Telegram%20and%20digital%20payment%20apps%20PhonePe%20and%20Paytm%20for%20allegedly%20abetting%20in%20the%20sale%20of%20child%20sex%20abuse%20material%2C%20or%20CSAM.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsunitha-krishnan-child-sex-abuse-material-telegram-paytm-phonepe-activists-case-against-telegram-paytm-for-enabling-child-sex-abuse-content-4575853%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsunitha-krishnan-child-sex-abuse-material-telegram-paytm-phonepe-activists-case-against-telegram-paytm-for-enabling-child-sex-abuse-content-4575853%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsunitha-krishnan-child-sex-abuse-material-telegram-paytm-phonepe-activists-case-against-telegram-paytm-for-enabling-child-sex-abuse-content-4575853%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Investor%20Fired%20From%20His%20Firm%20After%20He%20Calls%20For%20Sterilising%20Palestinians%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20venture%20capitalist%20has%20been%20fired%20from%20a%20US%20investment%20firm%20he%20cofounded%20after%20he%20made%20offensive%20remarks%20against%C2%A0Palestinians%20amid%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war.%C2%A0Kenneth%20Ballenegger%2C%20a%20founding%20partner%20at%20San%20Francisco%20VC%20firm%20Oyster%20Ventures%2C%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20war%2C%20Israel%20should%20handle%20Gaza%20like%20China%20handles%20Xinjiang.%20Full%20surveillance%20state.%20Re-education%20camps.%20Sterilizations.It's%20warranted%20and%20the%20only%20way%20to%20pacify%20the%20jihadi%20population.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20his%20controversial%20opinion%20was%20questioned%20by%20a%20former%20colleague%2C%20he%20made%20another%20offensive%20statement%20in%20response.%20He%20wrote%2C%20''They%20reproduce%20like%20rabbits%20and%20raise%20them%20to%20be%20terrorists%2C%20creating%20more%20poverty%20misery%2C%20and%20terrorism.%20Why%20should%20we%20allow%20that%3F%20The%20world%20would%20be%20a%20much%20better%20place%20if%20they%20didn't%20reproduce.''%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20his%20X%20profile%20private%20after%20his%20post%20was%20criticised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20the%20screenshots%20of%20the%20tweet%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3Ethis%20guy%20isn't%20some%20random%20employee%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cnhe%20is%20your%20co-founder%2C%20it%20very%20much%20reflects%20the%20values%20of%20your%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FtMQnBX4fKT%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FtMQnBX4fKT%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FRNYc8GuRN8%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FRNYc8GuRN8%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Matt%20Binder%20(%40MattBinder)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMattBinder%2Fstatus%2F1724125253415113040%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20several%20X%20users%20criticised%20his%20stance%2C%C2%A0Sophia%20Liao%2C%20Ballenegger's%20fellow%20co-founding%20partner%20at%20Oyster%20issued%20a%20statement%20on%20X%20distancing%20the%20company%20from%20his%20remarks.%20She%20wrote%2C%20''With%20the%20support%20of%20Oyster%20Ventures'%20leadership%20team%2C%20we%20have%20since%20made%20a%20decision%20to%20remove%20Kenneth%20Ballenegger%20as%20a%20partner%20in%20the%20firm.%20This%20process%20will%20take%20time%2C%20but%20please%20be%20assured%20that%20Kenneth%20has%20been%20suspended%20immediately%20and%20these%20proceedings%20are%20underway.%20''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22zxx%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F631bthiRVb%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F631bthiRVb%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Oyster%20Ventures%20(%40OysterVentures)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FOysterVentures%2Fstatus%2F1724290372158078984%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Liao%20continued%2C%20''On%20a%20personal%20note%2C%20as%20someone%20who%20survived%20and%20grew%20up%20under%20China's%20one-child%20policy%2C%20it's%20awful%20to%20see%20such%20a%20callous%20comparison%20made%20between%20such%20complex%20political%20environments.%20This%20perspective%20makes%20Kenneth's%20choice%20of%20words%20even%20more%20distressing%20to%20me.%E2%80%9D%20I've%20reached%20out%20to%20him%20directly%20to%20explain%20this%20and%20his%20immediate%20removal%20from%20the%20firm.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Oyster%20Ventures%20is%20headquartered%20in%20San%20Francisco.%20The%20company%20has%20invested%20in%20unicorn%20tech%20companies%20including%20e-commerce%20startup%20Bolt%2C%20online%20learning%20platform%20Masterclass%2C%20and%20gaming%20software%20company%20Conductive.AI%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthemessenger.com%2Fbusiness%2Fventure-capitalist-who-called-for-sterilizing-palestinians-is-put-on-track-to-be-fired%5C%22%3EThe%20Messenger.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20companies%20around%20the%20world%20have%20fired%20employees%20over%20offensive%20remarks%20related%20to%20the%20Israel-Gaza%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700046660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fhlibe4eg_kenneth-ballenegger_625x300_15_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-venture-capitalist-fired-from-his-firm-after-he-calls-for-sterilising-palestinians-4576036%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20shared%20a%20post%20on%20social%20media%20that%20said%20''Israel%20was%20warranted%20to%20handle%20Gaza%20by%20setting%20up%20''education%20camps%20and%20sterilizations.''%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-venture-capitalist-fired-from-his-firm-after-he-calls-for-sterilising-palestinians-4576036%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-venture-capitalist-fired-from-his-firm-after-he-calls-for-sterilising-palestinians-4576036%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-venture-capitalist-fired-from-his-firm-after-he-calls-for-sterilising-palestinians-4576036%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tenants%20and%20a%20top%20prosecutor%20have%20accused%20major%20landlords%20and%20a%20popular%20apartment-pricing%20site%20of%20colluding%20to%20inflate%20rents.%20A%20legal%20expert%20says%20it%20shows%20algorithmic%20collusion%20is%20no%20longer%20'science%20fiction.'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sign%20is%20posted%20in%20front%20of%20an%20apartment%20building%20with%20available%20rentals%20on%20June%2009%2C%202023%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6552a7a236d588dc55cfa8c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERent-settling%20algorithms%20used%20by%20landlords%20nationwide%20may%20be%20artificially%20increasing%20rents%20above%20market%20rates.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Sullivan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20big%20landlords%20are%20using%20algorithmic%20pricing%20systems%20to%20set%20rents%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20might%20be%20illegal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERealPage%2C%20which%20sells%20rent-setting%20software%2C%20and%20its%20clients%20are%20facing%20a%20slew%20of%20lawsuits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20DC%20attorney%20general%20is%20the%20latest%20to%20allege%20illegal%20collusion%20to%20set%20artificially%20high%20rents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYou're%20probably%20aware%20that%20a%20severe%20housing%20shortage%20has%20driven%20rents%20and%20home%20prices%20through%20the%20roof%20in%20recent%20years.%20Now%2C%20several%20lawsuits%20filed%20across%20the%20country%20contend%20that%20the%20algorithmic%20software%20some%20big%20landlords%20use%20to%20determine%20rents%20has%20artificially%20inflated%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20attorney%20general%2C%20Brian%20Schwalb%2C%20earlier%20this%20month%20became%20the%20first%20top%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3Eprosecutor%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Foag.dc.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2023-11%2FDC%2520OAG%2520RealPage%2520Complaint%2520-%2520Filed.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esue%20the%20real-estate%20tech%20company%20RealPage%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%2014%20of%20DC's%20biggest%20landlords%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20illegally%20colluding%20to%20set%20rent%20prices%20above%20competitive%20levels.%20RealPage%20and%20one%20of%20its%20competitors%2C%20Yardi%2C%20have%20been%20sued%20by%20renters%20in%20other%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERealPage%2C%20a%20Texas-based%20company%2C%20sells%20software%20called%20YieldStar%20that%20recommends%20apartment%20rent%20prices%20to%20its%20clients%20%E2%80%94%20landlords%20and%20property%20managers%20%E2%80%94%20based%20on%20nonpublic%20information%20it%20gathers%C2%A0in%20a%20given%20real-estate%20market.%20The%20AG's%20complaint%20says%20that%20RealPage%20and%20the%20landlords'%20%26quot%3Bcoordinated%20and%20anticompetitive%20conduct%20amounts%20to%20a%20District-wide%20housing%20cartel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20alleges%20that%20RealPage%20helped%20its%20landlord%20clients%C2%A0inflate%20rents%20by%20up%20to%207%25%20for%20about%2040%2C000%20apartments%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0mostly%20in%20large%2C%20multifamily%20buildings%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0across%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20legal%20expert%20said%20that%20based%20on%20the%20accusations%20in%20the%20suit%2C%20the%20company%20and%20its%20clients%20may%20have%20committed%20antitrust%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20promising%20higher%20prices%20by%20a%20small%20but%20significant%20amount%2C%20even%20though%20occupancy%20is%20going%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Maurice%20Stucke%2C%20a%20law%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Tennessee%20and%20a%20former%20DOJ%20antitrust%20division%20prosecutor%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BTypically%2C%20that's%20the%20telltale%20sign%20of%20collusion%2C%20whether%20actual%20collusion%20or%20what's%20called%20conscious%20parallelism%20or%20tacit%20collusion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERealPage%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%2C%20but%20the%20company%20has%20previously%20denied%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20seeking%20to%20draw%20a%20causal%20connection%20between%20revenue%20management%20software%20like%20ours%20and%20increases%20in%20market-wide%20rents%2C%20this%20copycat%20suit%20repeats%20the%20inaccuracies%20of%20predecessor%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20company%20communications%20officer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2023%2F11%2F02%2Fdc-housing-rent-antitrust-lawsuit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Axios%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERealPage%20significantly%20expanded%20in%202017%2C%20when%20the%20company%20bought%20its%20largest%20competitor%2C%20The%20Rainmaker%20Group%2C%20which%20also%20made%20rent-setting%20software.%20The%20Justice%20Department%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0which%20sharply%20reduced%20its%20antitrust%20prosecutions%20under%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0declined%20to%20challenge%20the%20merger%2C%20despite%20it%20raising%20alarms%20with%20DOJ%20staffers.%20RealPage's%20CEO%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Steve%20Winn%2C%20said%20the%20acquisition%20would%20allow%20the%20company%20to%20double%20the%20number%20of%20homes%20it%20set%20rent%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProPublica%20drew%20public%20attention%20to%20the%20company's%20practices%20when%20it%20published%20an%20explosive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.propublica.org%2Farticle%2Fyieldstar-rent-increase-realpage-rent%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Einvestigation%20in%20October%202022%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20revealing%20how%20RealPage%20executives%20explicitly%20advertised%20its%20goal%20of%20inflating%20rents%20above%20market%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20and%20its%20clients%20have%20since%20been%20sued%20in%20jurisdictions%20across%20the%20country%2C%20including%20Seattle%2C%20New%20York%2C%20Boston%2C%20and%20Colorado.%20More%20than%2020%20of%20these%20lawsuits%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Flegal%2Flitigation%2Frealpage-antitrust-lawsuits-over-rent-prices-consolidated-tennessee-2023-04-10%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewere%20consolidated%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20federal%20court%20in%20Nashville%20last%20spring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStucke%20said%20there%20were%20several%20notable%20allegations%20in%20the%20DC%20attorney%20general's%20complaint.%20The%20suit%20says%20that%20RealPage%20wouldn't%20allow%20landlords%20to%20reject%20the%20algorithm's%20recommendation%20for%20rent%2C%20except%20in%20%26quot%3Bextenuating%20circumstances%20such%20as%20a%20natural%20disaster.%26quot%3B%20This%20allegation%20is%20unusual%2C%20given%20that%20RealPage%20doesn't%20have%20any%20market%20power%20over%20its%20clients%2C%20Stucke%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20also%20allege%20that%20RealPage%20monitors%20the%20rents%20that%20its%20clients%20charge%20and%20disciplines%20landlords%20who%20don't%20adhere%20to%20its%20recommendations.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20RealPage%20sought%20to%20grow%20the%20cartel%20to%20maximize%20profits%2C%20it%20also%20understood%20the%20importance%20of%20universal%20adherence%20and%20was%20willing%20to%20expel%20an%20occasional%20cartel%20member%20to%20demonstrate%20its%20commitment%20to%20enforcement%20of%20the%20agreed-upon%20pricing%20scheme%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20that's%20the%20case%2C%20that's%20very%20much%20like%20a%20traditional%20cartel%2C%26quot%3B%20Stucke%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20discipline%20in%20the%20form%20of%20getting%20rid%20of%20a%20client%20is%20largely%20unnecessary%20because%20landlords%20used%20the%20RealPage-recommended%20rents%20more%20than%2090%25%20of%20the%20time%2C%20the%20complaint%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20suit%20says%20that%20rival%20landlords%20met%20with%20each%20other%20and%20encouraged%20competitors%20to%20use%20RealPage%2C%20another%20telltale%20sign%20of%20collusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20interesting%20thing%20here%20is%20why%20would%20landlords%20seek%20to%20recruit%20their%20rivals%20to%20a%20platform%2C%20unless%20they're%20expecting%20as%20a%20result%20of%20their%20joining%20this%20platform%20it's%20going%20to%20help%20them%20further%20increase%20rents%3F%26quot%3B%20Stucke%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECongress%20and%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20have%20also%20gotten%20involved.%20House%20and%20Senate%20lawmakers%20began%20raising%20concerns%20about%20RealPage%20and%20its%20effect%20on%20the%20real-estate%20market%20last%20year.%20Last%20fall%2C%2017%20Democratic%20House%20members%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.propublica.org%2Farticle%2Fyieldstar-rent-increase-realpage-lawmakers-collusion%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eurged%20the%20DOJ%20and%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20investigate%20RealPage.%20Soon%20after%2C%20Democratic%20senators%C2%A0sent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23309884-08c76dea4bc4f963258bc401335e6569letter-to-aag-kanter-re-realpage-11422%3Fresponsive%3D1%26title%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ea%20letter%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20DOJ's%20antitrust%20division%20urging%20it%20to%20investigate%20whether%20the%20company%20had%20created%20%26quot%3Ba%20cartel%20to%20artificially%20inflate%20rental%20rates%20in%20multifamily%20residential%20buildings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20last%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.propublica.org%2Farticle%2Fyieldstar-realpage-rent-doj-investigation-antitrust%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProPublica%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20DOJ%20had%20begun%20an%20investigation%20into%20RealPage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlgorithmic%20collusion%20is%20relatively%20new.%20Stucke%20has%20been%20researching%20and%20writing%20about%20the%20phenomenon%20since%202016%2C%20but%20it's%20only%20recently%20been%20widely%20understood%20and%20identified.%20Computer%20scientists%20and%20economists%20say%20that%20the%20algorithms%20could%20tacitly%20collude%20without%20any%20intentional%20intervention%20by%20people%20or%20any%20agreement%20to%20conspire%20to%20raise%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20first%20wrote%20about%20it%2C%20some%20people%20dismissed%20it%20as%20science%20fiction%2C%20that%20it's%20unlikely%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20Stucke%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomics.yale.edu%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fclark_acex_jan_2021.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20empirical%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%202021%20concluded%20that%20prices%20can%20rise%20above%20competitive%20levels%20when%20between%20two%20and%20seven%20competitors%20in%20a%20given%20field%20use%20algorithms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20these%20allegations%20are%20true%2C%20then%20we%20have%20a%20real%20problem%20on%20our%20hands%2C%20and%20not%20just%20in%20housing%20but%20in%20many%20other%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20Stucke%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-apartment-rent-price-setting-landlords-realpage-lawsuit-illegal-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700046421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6552a7e158cf5fbccb95e822%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsi