collection-target-cbdt-123111500624_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Once%20Among%20Country's%20Most%20Influential%2C%20Subrata%20Roy%20Leaves%20Behind%20a%20Controversial%20Legacy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15155744%2FF-8ujsCW4AA6gOA.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Subrata%20Roy%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20vast%20business%20empire%20Sahara%20Group%2C%20died%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20November%2014%2C%20following%20an%20extended%20battle%20with%20complications%20arising%20from%20metastatic%20malignancy%2C%20hypertension%20and%20diabetes.%20Roy%20was%2075.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20was%20admitted%20to%20Kokilaben%20Dhirubhai%20Ambani%20Hospital%20%26amp%3B%20Medical%20Research%20Institute%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20Sunday%20after%20his%20health%20deteriorated.%20Roy%20is%20survived%20by%20wife%20Swapna%20Roy%20and%20two%20sons%2C%20Sushanto%20and%20Seemanto.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUntil%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20Roy%20was%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20most%20influential%20businessmen%20in%20the%20country.%20Mired%20in%20controversies%2C%20facing%20multiple%20regulatory%20and%20legal%20battles%2C%20his%20group%20firms%20accused%20of%20circumventing%20regulations%20with%20Ponzi%20schemes%2C%20in%20the%20recent%20years%2C%20Roy%20was%20only%20known%20to%20allegedly%20having%20duped%20investors%20from%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERoy%20made%20a%20modest%20start%20in%201978%20with%20a%20capital%20of%20only%20Rs%202%2C000.%20In%20less%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20build%20Sahara%20India%20over%20the%20decades.%20The%20Group%2C%20as%20per%20the%20claims%20made%20on%20the%20official%20website%2C%20has%209%20crore%20investors%20and%20customers%2C%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20Rs%20259%2C900%20crore%2C%205%2C000%20establishments%20and%2030%2C970%20acres%20of%20land%20bank.%20According%20to%20Reuters%2C%20Sahara%E2%80%99s%20assets%20at%20one%20point%20in%20time%20included%20New%20York%E2%80%99s%20Plaza%20Hotel%20and%20the%20Grosvenor%20House%20in%20London.%20Subrata%20Roy%20was%20once%20also%20a%20co-owner%20of%20the%20former%20Force%20India%20Formula%20One%20team.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMillions%20of%20poor%20Indians%20from%20%3Cem%3Emofussil%3C%2Fem%3E%20parts%20deposited%20money%20in%20his%20company.%20These%20were%20mostly%20illiterate%20with%20zero%20to%20minimum%20access%20to%20formal%20banking%20services.%20The%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20eventually%20stepped%20in%20and%20Roy%E2%80%99s%20companies%20were%20accused%20of%20collection%20of%20over%20Rs%2024%2C000%20crore%20from%20over%20three%20crore%20individuals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202004%2C%20his%20company%20had%20over%201.2%20million%20work%20force%20%E2%80%93%20it%20was%20only%20second%20to%20the%20Indian%20Railways.%20His%20name%20featured%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3ETIME%3C%2Fem%3E%20magazine%20that%20year.%20His%20business%20%E2%80%93%20spread%20across%20retail%2C%20real%20estate%20and%20financial%20services%20sectors%20soon%20got%20embroiled%20in%20a%20legal%20tussle%20with%20the%20SEBI%20after%20the%20market%20regulator%20in%202011%20ordered%20Sahara%20India%20Real%20Estate%20Corporation%20Ltd%20(SIRECL)%20and%20Sahara%20Housing%20Investment%20Corporation%20Ltd%20(SHICL)%20to%20refund%20the%20money%20raised%20from%20investors%20through%20certain%20bonds%20known%20as%20Optionally%20Fully%20Convertible%20Bonds%20(OFCDs)%20that%20was%20later%20ruled%20to%20be%20illegal.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fsaharashri-and-the-supremes%5C%22%3ESaharashri%20and%20the%20Supremes%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERoy%2C%20however%2C%20with%20his%20close%20political%20connections%2C%20mostly%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20enjoyed%20both%20political%20and%20Bollywood%20clout.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStarting%202010%20began%20his%20slow%20downfall.%20In%202011%2C%20SEBI%20ordered%20two%20Sahara%20Group%20firms%20%E2%80%93%20Sahara%20India%20Real%20Estate%20Corporation%20Ltd%20(SIREL)%20and%20Sahara%20Housing%20Investment%20Corporation%20Ltd%20(SHICL)%20%E2%80%93%20to%20refund%20the%20money%20raised%20from%20nearly%203%20crore%20investors%20through%20certain%20bonds%20known%20as%20Optionally%20Fully%20Convertible%20Bonds%20(OFCDs).%20SEBI%20had%20accused%20his%20two%20companies%20of%20raising%20the%20funds%20by%20violating%20the%20market%20regulator%E2%80%99s%20rules.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202012%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20upheld%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20directions%20asking%20the%20two%20firms%20to%20refund%20the%20money%20collected%20from%20investors%20with%2015%20per%20cent%20interest.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202014%2C%20a%20local%20court%20sent%20Roy%20to%20jail%20for%20not%20paying%20an%20outstanding%20amount%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore.%20His%20release%20was%20conditioned%20on%20return%20of%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore%20in%20cash%20and%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore%20by%20way%20of%20bank%20guarantee.%20Roy%20spent%20two%20years%20in%20jail%2C%20before%20he%20was%20finally%20released%20on%20a%20parole.%20But%20this%20release%20was%20short%20lived.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20soon%20sent%20him%20to%20jail%2C%20only%20for%20him%20to%20be%20later%20released%20on%20bail.%20SEBI%2C%20however%2C%20contested%20the%20bail%20in%202020.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20detailed%20investigative%20report%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fvantage%2Fmodi-receive-over-55-crore-from-sahara-group-chief-minister-gujarat%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epublished%20in%20%3Cem%3ECaravan%3C%2Fem%3E%20magazine%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%202016%2C%20journalist%20Paranjoy%20Guha%20Thakurta%20had%20pointed%20to%20over%20Rs%2055%20crore%20from%20the%20Sahara%20Group%20allegedly%20received%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20when%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat.%20In%20the%20report%2C%20Guha%20Thakurta%20wrote%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20documents%2C%20which%20have%20been%20doing%20the%20rounds%20in%20Delhi%20for%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20suggest%20that%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20Modi%E2%80%94along%20with%20a%20number%20of%20important%20politicians%E2%80%94was%20paid%20large%20amounts%20of%20cash%20by%20individuals%20associated%20with%20Subrata%20Roy%2C%20the%20founder-chairman%20of%20the%20Sahara%20India%20Group.%20These%20documents%20also%20suggest%20that%20the%20recipients%20of%20such%20favours%20included%2C%20among%20others%3A%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%3B%20Raman%20Singh%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Chhattisgarh%3B%20Shaina%20NC%2C%20the%20treasurer%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20party%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%3B%20Sheila%20Dikshit%2C%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20Delhi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20documents%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ECaravan%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20claimed%2C%20bore%20%E2%80%9Can%20uncanny%20resemblance%20to%20the%20infamous%20Jain%20Hawala%20dairies%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%201996%2C%20these%20dairies%2C%20which%20came%20into%20the%20possession%20of%20the%20CBI%2C%20indicated%20those%20associated%20with%20businessperson%20Surinder%20Kumar%20Jain%20and%20his%20brother%20had%20made%20payments%20to%20a%20host%20of%20important%20political%20personalities%20such%20as%20L.K.%20Advani%2C%20Madhavrao%20Scindia%2C%20Balram%20Jakhar%2C%20V.C.%20Shukla%2C%20Madan%20Lal%20Khurana%2C%20P.%20Shiv%20Shankar%20and%20Arif%20Mohammed%20Khan%2C%20among%20others