0href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fsecrecy-and-no-tax-reason-why-indians-look-at-cyprus-9027035%2F%5C%22%3ECyprus%20Confidential%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20worldwide%20offshore%20probe%20of%203.6%20million%20documents%20in%20English%20and%20Greek%2C%20exposing%20a%20trail%20of%20companies%20established%20in%20Cyprus%20as%20a%20tax%20haven%20by%20global%20elites%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexpress-exclusive%2Fcracking-cyprus-confidential-eu-state-gave-investors-tax-haven-secrecy-and-a-golden-passport-9026642%2F%5C%22%3ERussian%20oligarchs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CCyprus%20Investment%20Programme%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgolden%20passport%E2%80%9D%20scheme%20was%20launched%20in%202007.%20It%20enabled%20financially%20prominent%20individuals%20to%20obtain%20Cypriot%20citizenship%2C%20thereby%20attracting%20foreign%20direct%20investments%20into%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%2066%20Indians%20who%20got%20their%20%E2%80%9Cgolden%20passport%E2%80%9D%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fvinod-gautam-adani-u-turn%5C%22%3EVinod%20Adani%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Gautam%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20elder%20brother%20who%20came%20under%20spotlight%20in%20Hindenburg%20Research%E2%80%99s%20investigation%3B%20Pankaj%20Oswal%2C%20chairman%20and%20founder%20of%20Burrup%20Holdings%20Limited%2C%20and%20real%20estate%20baron%20Surendra%20Hiranandani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20European%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20website%2C%20Cyprus%20repealed%20its%20%E2%80%9Cgolden%20passport%E2%80%9D%20scheme%20and%20stopped%20receiving%20new%20applications%20on%20November%201%2C%202020.%20However%2C%20it%20continued%20to%20process%20pending%20applications.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20European%20Commission%20decided%20to%20send%20a%20reasoned%20opinion%20to%20Cyprus%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fec.europa.eu%2Fcommission%2Fpresscorner%2Fdetail%2Fen%2Finf_21_2743%5C%22%3EJune%209%2C%202021%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Since%20then%2C%20Cyprus%20stopped%20processing%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20was%20scrapped%20due%20to%20alleged%20misuse%20and%20for%20allowing%20persons%20with%20criminal%20charges%2C%20dubious%20character%20and%20PEPs%20(politically%20exposed%20persons)%20to%20acquire%20Cyprus%20passports%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENames%20of%20a%20total%20of%2083%20individuals%20were%20flagged%20for%20review%20and%20possible%20revocation.%20A%20majority%20of%20them%20were%20earlier%20citizens%20of%20Russia%20and%2C%20according%20to%20the%20data%2C%20most%20were%20marked%20for%20applications%20bearing%20%E2%80%9Cfalse%20statement%20by%20the%20investors%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20daily%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Commission%20appointed%20by%20the%20Attorney%20General%20of%20Cyprus%2C%20Georgios%20Savvides%2C%20in%20September%202020%20and%20headed%20by%20retired%20Supreme%20Court%20Chairman%2C%20Myron%20Nicolatos%2C%20made%20the%20list%20of%20these%20possible%20revocations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Cyprus%20government%20has%20not%20yet%20officially%20revealed%20how%20many%20of%20those%20under%20the%20scanner%20had%20their%20Cypriot%20citizenships%20revoked%2C%20the%20daily%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERevocations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20there%20is%20only%20one%20Indian%20on%20the%20list%20of%20proposed%20revocations%20of%20Cypriot%20passports%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Fnsel-case-ed-attaches-defaulters-property-in-dubai%2Farticle65523301.ece%5C%22%3EAnubhav%20Aggarwal%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20businessman%20whose%20%E2%80%9Cgolden%20passport%E2%80%9D%20was%20approved%20within%20four%20months%20on%20November%202%2C%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nicolatos%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20inquiry%20report%20states%20that%20Aggarwal%20was%20implicated%20in%20the%20National%20Spot%20Exchange%20Limited%20(NSEL)%20scam%20and%20that%20he%20failed%20to%20mention%20his%20links%20with%20the%20suspect%20companies%20in%20his%20application%20for%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20%E2%80%9Ckey%20accused%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20Rs%203%2C600%20crore%20NSEL%20scam%2C%20Aggarwal%20faced%20arrest%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20in%20August%202020.%20In%20June%202020%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20seized%20his%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAggarwal%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20Indian%20obtaining%20Cypriot%20citizenship%20under%20the%20now-defunct%20investment%20scheme%2C%20despite%20legal%20issues%20with%20Indian%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENesamanimaran%20Muthu%2C%20better%20known%20as%20MGM%20Maran%2C%20a%20Tamil%20Nadu-based%20businessman%20and%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Mercantile%20Bank%20Limited%2C%20acquired%20Cypriot%20citizenship%20in%202016.%20His%20application%20was%20cleared%20in%20just%20two%20months.%20In%202017%2C%20his%20two%20children%20also%20got%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202022%2C%20the%20ED%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbfsi.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findustry%2Fed-attaches-assets-worth-rs-205-36-cr-of-chennai-based-firm%2F96538226%5C%22%3Eattached%3C%2Fa%3E%20assets%20worth%20Rs%20200%20crores%20of%20his%20Maran%E2%80%99s%20company%2C%20Agrifurane%20Industries%20Private%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20probe%20agency%20had%20issued%20a%20media%20release%20saying%20that%20assets%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%20293%20crore%20had%20been%20attached%20by%20them%20since%20an%20equivalent%20foreign%20investment%20had%20been%20made%20by%20Maran%20in%20two%20companies%20in%20Singapore%20without%20approval%20of%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20also%20mentioned%20Maran%E2%80%99s%20Cypriot%20citizenship%20in%20an%20official%20release.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20order%20to%20escape%20the%20reach%20of%20Indian%20laws%2C%20MGM%20Maran%20surrendered%20his%20Indian%20citizenship.%20Not%20only%20that%2C%20it%20was%20also%20found%20that%20MGM%20Maran%20also%20started%20transferring%20his%20wealth%20from%20India%20to%20overseas%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20the%20same%20out%20of%20reach%20of%20the%20Indian%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20in%20the%20garb%20of%20overseas%20direct%20investments%20from%20Southern%20Agrifurane%20Industries%20Private%20Limited%20(his%20flagship%20company)%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ED%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Cyprus%20Confidential%20investigation%20by%20OCCRP%20and%20other%20media%20partners%2C%20the%20Cyprus%20Ministry%20of%20Interior%20said%20that%20they%20have%20decided%20on%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20deprivation%20of%20citizenship%20of%20233%20individuals%20and%20of%20them%2C%2068%20individuals%20are%20investors%20and%20165%20are%20family%20members%20of%20the%20investors.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAllegations%20over%20tax%20evasion%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20January%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhindenburgresearch.com%2Fadani%2F%5C%22%3EHindenburg%20Research%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20detailed%20Vinod%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20offshore%20holdings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%2C%20which%20included%20downloading%20and%20cataloguing%20the%20entire%20Mauritius%20corporate%20registry%2C%20uncovered%20that%20Vinod%20Adani%2C%20through%20several%20close%20associates%2C%20manages%20a%20vast%20labyrinth%20of%20offshore%20shell%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20it%20identified%2038%20Mauritius%20shell%20entities%20controlled%20by%20Vinod%20Adani%20or%20close%20associates.%20It%20also%20identified%20entities%20that%20were%20also%20%E2%80%9Csurreptitiously%20controlled%E2%80%9D%20by%20Vinod%20Adani%20in%20Cyprus%2C%20the%20UAE%2C%20Singapore%2C%20and%20several%20Caribbean%20Islands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20these%20shell%20companies%2C%20Vinod%20Adani%2C%20per%20the%20report%2C%20was%20key%20in%20managing%20%E2%80%9Ca%20vast%20labyrinth%20of%20offshore%20shell%20entities%E2%80%9D%20to%20facilitate%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20manipulation%2C%20it%20said%2C%20was%20helping%20the%20Adani%20companies%20maintain%20their%20appearance%20of%20financial%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fcompany%2Fcorporate-trends%2Fadani-addresses-hindenburg-allegations-head-on-at-agm-says-vested-interests-wrote-report-to-hurt-company%2Farticleshow%2F101845922.cms%5C%22%3Ehas%20denied%3C%2Fa%3E%20all%20these%20allegations%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccalculated%20attack%20on%20India%2C%20the%20independence%2C%20integrity%20and%20quality%20of%20Indian%20institutions%2C%20and%20the%20growth%20story%20and%20ambition%20of%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20after%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%2C%20Vinod%20Adani%2C%20who%20mostly%20occupied%20the%20back%20seat%20in%20business%20operations%20of%20Adani%20Group%2C%20came%20under%20the%20spotlight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fvinod-gautam-adani-u-turn%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Vinod%20Adani%20%E2%80%9Cdoes%20not%20hold%20any%20managerial%20position%20in%20any%20Adani%20listed%20entities%20or%20their%20subsidiaries%20and%20has%20no%20role%20in%20their%20day%20to%20day%20affairs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20it%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Adani%20Group%20and%20Vinod%20Adani%20should%20be%20seen%20as%20one.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVinod%20Adani%20is%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98promoter%20group%E2%80%99%20of%20various%20listed%20entities%20within%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20clarified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20Indians%20who%20obtained%20Cypriot%20citizenship%20are%20industrialist%20Pankaj%20Oswal%20and%20his%20wife%20Radhika%20Oswal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPankaj%20Oswal%2C%20is%20founder%20of%20Burrup%20Holdings%20Limited%2C%20a%20liquid%20ammonium%20manufacturer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20in%20the%20news%20recently%20for%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-tycoon-pankaj-oswal-buys-one-of-the-worlds-most-expensive-houses-for-rs-1-649-crore-in-switzerland-11687886475271.html%5C%22%3E%20purchasing%3C%2Fa%3E%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20expensive%20houses%20in%20Switzerland%20for%20%24200%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOtis%20data%20contains%20numerous%20documents%20related%20to%20Cyprol%20Limited%2C%20the%20company%20established%20by%20Pankaj%20Oswal%20in%20Cyprus%2C%20as%20well%20as%20details%20of%20his%20citizenship%20application%20and%20final%20approval.%20The%20Oswals%20applied%20for%20citizenship%20on%20April%2028%2C%202017%2C%20and%20it%20was%20granted%20almost%20a%20year%20later%20on%20April%204%2C%202018%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20once%20Pankaj%20Oswal%20obtained%20his%20Cypriot%20citizenship%2C%20he%20shut%20down%20Cyprol%20Limited%20%E2%80%94%20proof%20of%20this%20is%20the%20authorisation%20he%20signed%20as%20the%20Ultimate%20Beneficial%20Owner%20(UBO)%20of%20the%20company%20for%20ConnectedSky%2C%20on%20March%2022%2C%202019%20to%20strike%20off%20the%20company%20from%20the%20Cyprus%20registry%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConnectedSky%20is%20one%20of%20the%20six%20financial%20service%20providers%20which%20over%20270%20investigative%20reporters%20examined%20for%20the%20Cyprus%20Confidential%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202016%2C%20the%20couple%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fcompanies%2Fpankaj-radhika-oswal-told-not-to-leave-australia-over-tax-claims-report-116042200318_1.html%5C%22%3Ewas%20barred%20indefinitely%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fmagazines%2Fpanache%2Faustralia-slashes-190-mn-unpaid-tax-claim-for-indian-couple%2Farticleshow%2F52618960.cms%5C%22%3Efrom%20leaving%3C%2Fa%3E%20Australia%20over%20tax%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20it%20is%20expected%20that%20Cyprus%20Confidential%20will%20compel%20regulatory%20and%20investigative%20agencies%20to%20unveil%20yet%20another%20layer%2C%20like%20they%20did%20after%20previous%20global%20investigations%20revealed%20substantial%20instances%20of%20tax%20avoidance%20and%20evasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700042440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15150641%2Fimage-1504.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fvinod-adani-among-66-indians-who-got-cypruss-golden-passport-between-2014-and-2020-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Also%20known%20as%20the%20'Cyprus%20Investment%20Programme'%2C%20the%20'golden%20passport'%20scheme%20was%20launched%20in%202007.%20It%20enabled%20financially%20prominent%20individuals%20to%20obtain%20Cypriot%20citizenship%2C%20thereby%20attracting%20foreign%20direct%20investments%20into%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fvinod-adani-among-66-indians-who-got-cypruss-golden-passport-between-2014-and-2020-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Has%20Five%20Times%20The%20Number%20Of%20Schools%20Than%20China%3A%20Niti%20Aayog%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20recently%20released%20Niti%20Aayog%20report%20titled%20Learnings%20from%20Large-scale%20Transformation%20in%20School%20Education%2C%20India%20continues%20to%20have%20five%20times%20the%20number%20of%20schools%20than%20China%20for%20the%20same%20enrolment%20of%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20recent%20report%20published%20by%20Reuters%20dozens%20of%20international%20and%20private%20schools%20in%20China%20are%20closing%20or%20merging%20because%20of%20tighter%20regulation%2C%20a%20slowing%20economy%20and%20dwindling%20foreign%20student%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20further%20cited%20that%20in%202020%20there%20were%20around%20180%2C000%20private%20education%20institutions%20nationwide%20which%20accounted%20for%20more%20than%20a%20third%20of%20all%20education%20institutions%20in%20China.%20These%20schools%20had%2055.6%20million%20students'%20enrollment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20international%20schools%2C%20which%20can%20only%20enroll%20students%20with%20foreign%20passports%2C%20have%20mostly%20seen%20student%20numbers%20decline%20due%20to%20expatriates%20from%20countries%20leaving%20after%20the%20pandemic%20and%20amid%20rising%20geopolitical%20tensions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20rapid%20expansion%20of%20schools%20prior%20to%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20drove%20a%20surge%20of%20privately%20run%20bilingual%20schools%20in%20China%20offering%20a%20western%20exam%20curriculum.%20The%20business%20stumbled%20later%20as%20Beijing%20imposed%20new%20rules%20in%202021%20and%20cracked%20down%20on%20the%20private%20tutoring%20business%2C%20aimed%20at%20easing%20pressure%20on%20children%20and%20lowering%20family%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20Reuters%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELow%20enrollments%20in%20Indian%20schools%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnAs%20per%20the%20Niti%20Aayog%20report%2C%20over%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20primary%20schools%20across%20many%20states%20in%20India%20have%20an%20enrolment%20of%20less%20than%2060.%20The%20cost%20of%20such%20sub-scale%20schools%20in%20the%20form%20of%20extensive%20multi-grade%20teaching%2C%20lack%20of%20a%20student%20and%20parent%20community%20that%20can%20demand%20account%20ability%2C%20poor%20infrastructure%20and%20the%20same%201-2%20teachers%20also%20handling%20all%20administrative%20responsibilities%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20headmasters%2F%20principals%2C%20etc%20is%20very%20high.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20report%20suggested%20school%20mergers%20as%20a%20solution%20to%20addressing%20the%20lack%20%C2%A0of%20enrollments%20in%20schools.%20As%20per%20the%20report%2C%20such%20solution%20has%20been%20executed%20across%20SATH-E%20states%20and%20have%20given%20favorable%20results%20in%20filling%20up%20the%20enrolments%20in%20schools.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20often%20a%20perceived%20risk%20around%20impact%20of%20mergers%20on%20access.%20However%2C%20third%20party%20studies%20in%20SATH-E%20have%20also%20demonstrated%20that%20when%20executed%20rigorously%20the%20benefits%20of%20mergers%20are%20largely%20positive%20and%20can%20lead%20to%20improved%20learning%20outcomes%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20mergers%2C%20the%20states%20can%20also%20develop%20a%20set%20of%20large%20schools%20with%20at%20least%2010-20%20per%20cent%20spread%20across%20the%20state.%20These%20schools%20can%20be%20integrated%20K-12%20schools%20and%20should%20provide%20transport%20so%20that%20all%20students%20can%20equitably%20access%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20been%20recommended%20in%20the%20NEP%20too%20with%20the%20call%20to%20setup%20large%20school%20complexes.%20The%20report%20documents%20details%20for%20how%20school%20consolidation%20efforts%20were%20undertaken%20in%20all%20three%20Project%20SATH-E%20states%20and%20their%20learnings.%20The%20report%20also%20has%20information%20about%20the%20efforts%20to%20develop%20leader%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700042400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-10%2Fpfh49muk_china-schools-reuters_625x300_23_October_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Findia-has-five-times-the-number-of-schools-than-china-niti-aayog-report-4575985%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20per%20the%20Niti%20Aay