2Fstatus%2F1724424806852919602%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Tuesday%20evening%2C%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Supriya%20Shrinate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FINCIndia%2Fstatus%2F1724417387313697136%5C%22%3Equestioned%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20ED%20and%20CBI%20in%20the%20case%20and%20demanded%20to%20know%20when%20Tomar%20would%20resign.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20are%20we%20waiting%20for%20now%20after%20the%20revelations%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Devendra%20Singh%20Tomar%3F%20The%20person%20himself%20is%20saying%20that%20all%20the%20transactions%20were%20done%20in%20cash%20and%20this%20matter%20is%20not%20of%20Rs%20100-200%20crore%20but%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20second%20video%20involving%20Devendra%2C%20who%20is%20Tomar%E2%80%99s%20elder%20son%20had%20gone%20viral.%20In%20it%2C%20he%20is%20allegedly%20seen%20talking%20to%20a%20middleman.%20In%20the%20video%2C%20they%20appear%20to%20be%20discussing%20transactions%20worth%20hundreds%20of%20crores%20of%20rupees.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20video%20was%20a%206-minute%20and%2029-second%20clip%20created%20by%20combining%20two%20WhatsApp%20calls%20(a%20video%20call%20and%20an%20audio%20call)%2C%20in%20which%20transactions%20worth%20crores%20of%20rupees%20and%20their%20transfer%20to%20multiple%20bank%20accounts%20were%20allegedly%20discussed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20second%20video%20was%20a%201-minute%20and%2035-second%20long%20clip%20in%20which%20Devendra%20is%20seen%20speaking%20on%20a%20WhatsApp%20video%20call%20to%20the%20same%20middleman%20with%20whom%20he%20was%20speaking%20in%20the%20earlier%20viral%20video.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second%20video%20was%20released%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Bhopal%20on%20November%2013.%20Congress%20national%20spokesperson%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20assembly%20election%20media%20in-charge%20Dr.%20Ragini%20Nayak%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20videos%20of%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%E2%80%99s%20son%20Devendra%20Tomar%20going%20viral%20are%20giving%20clear%20evidence%20that%20along%20with%20%E2%80%9850%25%20commission%E2%80%99%2C%20black%20money%20has%20also%20become%20synonymous%20with%20BJP%20leaders.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20been%20continuously%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20government%20of%20the%20state%20of%20charging%20a%20%E2%80%9C50%25%20commission%E2%80%9D%20in%20public%20works%20%E2%80%93%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20in%20the%20video%20clip%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20second%20video%20available%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Devendra%20and%20the%20alleged%20middleman%20are%20seen%20talking%20on%20a%20video%20call.%20Devendra%20Tomar%20can%20be%20seen%20on%20the%20screen%20of%20the%20middleman%E2%80%99s%20phone.%20The%20middleman%20is%20heard%20telling%20him%2C%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20month%20their%20CA%20will%20tell%20us%20whether%20it%20is%20Rs%2050%20crore%2C%20100%2C%20500%2C%20or%20how%20much%20it%20is%E2%80%A6%20So%2C%20we%20have%20to%20take%20it%20every%20month.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20this%20Devendra%20is%20heard%20replying%2C%20%E2%80%9COkay%2C%20no%20problem.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDevendra%3A%20%E2%80%98How%20much%20will%20they%20give%20for%20the%20first%20one%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMiddleman%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20quoted%20250%20for%20the%20first%20one.%20His%20CA%20will%20meet%20my%20bank%20manager%20today%E2%80%A6%20because%20it%20will%20be%20converted%20from%20there%20and%20will%20be%20transferred%20to%20you%20and%20then%20you%20can%20send%20it%20to%20Munedo%20however%20you%20want.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDevendra%3A%20%E2%80%9CGet%20it%20transferred%20in%20your%20account%2C%20we%20will%20send%20them%20after%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERegarding%20Munedo%20(which%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20company%20of%20some%20sort)%2C%20the%20middleman%20advises%20Devendra%20to%20keep%20at%20least%2050%25%20of%20his%20stake.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDevendra%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20keep%20it%2C%20no%20problem%E2%80%A6once%20the%20money%20becomes%20proper%2C%20we%20will%20do%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMiddleman%3A%20%E2%80%9CLet%20me%20tell%20them%20that%20we%20are%20ready.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESilence%20in%20the%20BJP%20camp%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20Congress%20president%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20targeted%20the%20BJP%20over%20the%20video%20in%20a%20public%20meeting%20on%20Monday%20and%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CDid%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20take%20action%20against%20Tomar%20ji%E2%80%99s%20son%3F%20Did%20he%20deploy%20the%20CBI%2C%20ED%20or%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department%20after%20him%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccusing%20the%20BJP%20government%20of%20the%20state%20of%20taking%2050%25%20commission%2C%20Gandhi%20also%20listed%20the%20names%20of%20various%20scams%20that%20took%20place%20during%20its%20tenure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%E2%80%99s%20national%20spokesperson%20Nayak%20also%20called%20it%20a%20transaction%20of%20%E2%80%98black%20money%E2%80%99%20and%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20PM%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20slogan%20against%20corruption%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ENa%20khaunga%20and%20na%20khane%20doonga%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20(which%20literally%20means%20%E2%80%98neither%20will%20I%20eat%2C%20nor%20let%20anyone%20else%20eat%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20figuratively%20refers%20to%20curbing%20corruption).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENayak%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20of%20them%20are%20flourishing%20under%20the%20patronage%20of%20Modi%20ji%20and%20when%20he%20said%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ena%20khaunga%20na%20khane%20doonga%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20he%20actually%20meant%20onions%20and%20tomatoes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20further%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20would%20Modi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20be%20silent%20if%20that%20were%20not%20the%20case%3F%20Why%20has%20Shivraj%20Singh%20gone%20mum%20on%20this%20issue%3F%20Their%20silence%20indicates%20confession.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENarendra%20Singh%20Tomar%20was%20the%20Union%20Minister%20of%20Steel%20and%20Mining%20between%202014%20and%202019.%20It%20is%20claimed%20that%20this%20video%20is%20from%20that%20period.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20word%20mining%20was%20also%20mentioned%20in%20the%20first%20video%20where%20at%20one%20point%20the%20middleman%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20asked%20me%20to%20send%20it%20(presumably%20money)%20where%20I%20had%20to%2C%20because%20I%20have%20not%20told%20(them)%20anyone%E2%80%99s%20name%20%E2%80%93%20where%20does%20the%20money%20go%E2%80%A6%20He%20has%20a%20trading%20firm%20and%20mining%20(company)%20in%20Rajasthan%E2%80%A6%20and%20the%20Mohali%20guy%20is%20a%20land%20dealer%2C%20he%20deals%20with%20politicians%20and%20officials%20for%20land%E2%80%A6%20all%20this%20liquid%20(money)%20comes%20from%20there.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERegarding%20the%20first%20viral%20video%2C%20some%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20said%20video%20could%20be%20about%20five%20to%20seven%20years%20old%2C%20perhaps%20from%20the%20time%20when%20Tomar%20was%20the%20Union%20minister.%20They%20cited%20Devendra%E2%80%99s%20thick%20hair%20as%20proof%20and%20claimed%20the%20footage%20had%20been%20preserved%2C%20so%20that%20it%20could%20be%20used%20at%20the%20right%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20first%20video%20surfaced%2C%20Devendra%20called%20it%20fake%20and%20fabricated%20and%20said%20that%20he%20would%20file%20a%20complaint%20against%20it%20to%20the%20Morena%20Superintendent%20of%20Police.%20On%20the%20complaint%20of%20Devendra%2C%20a%20case%20in%20this%20regard%20was%20also%20registered%20at%20the%20Civil%20Lines%20police%20station%20of%20Morena.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0tried%20to%20contact%20Civil%20Lines%20police%20station%20in-charge%20Veeresh%20Kushwaha%20regarding%20the%20progress%20in%20the%20investigation%20of%20the%20case%2C%20but%20could%20not%20reach%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20other%20than%20Tomar%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20central%20leadership%20as%20well%20as%20state%20level%20leaders%20have%20not%20given%20any%20specific%20reaction%20to%20the%20entire%20episode%20of%20the%20viral%20video%20that%20has%20been%20circulating%20for%20more%20than%20a%20week.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20now%20a%20possibility%20that%20these%20videos%20may%20create%20significant%20roadblocks%20on%20Tomar%E2%80%99s%20possible%20chief%20ministerial%20ambitions%20.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETomar%20has%20two%20sons%20%E2%80%93%20the%20elder%20son%20is%20Devendra%20while%20Prabal%20Pratap%20Singh%20Tomar%20is%20the%20younger%20son.%20In%20the%20Gwalior-Morena%20region%2C%20which%20has%20been%20his%20constituency%20and%20bastion%2C%20the%20two%20brothers%20are%20popularly%20known%20as%20Ramu%20Bhaiya%20and%20Raghu%20Bhaiya%20respectively.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYoung%20BJP%20workers%20in%20Gwalior%20flock%20around%20Tomar%E2%80%99s%20sons%20and%20are%20known%20to%20raise%20slogans%20of%20%E2%80%9Clong%20live%20Ramu%20Bhaiya%20and%20Raghu%20Bhaiya.%E2%80%9D%20Devendra%20or%20Ramu%20Bhaiya%20is%20also%20the%20vice-president%20of%20Hockey%20India.%20In%20any%20public%20event%2C%20the%20two%20brothers%20are%20honoured%20the%20way%20an%20MP%2C%20MLA%20or%20minister%20would%20be.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20Tomar%E2%80%99s%20ground%20work%20in%20his%20constituency%20is%20managed%20by%20his%20sons.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDevendra%E2%80%99s%20name%20had%20also%20come%20up%20as%20a%20ticket%20contender%20in%20this%20assembly%20election%20and%20there%20was%20speculation%20about%20him%20being%20selected%20as%20BJP%20candidate%20from%20Dimani%20or%20Gwalior%20East.%20However%2C%20the%20party%20fielded%20his%20father%2C%20the%20elder%20Tomar%2C%20from%20Dimani.%20Due%20to%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20policy%20of%20%E2%80%98one%20family%2C%20one%20ticket%E2%80%99%2C%20Devendra%E2%80%99s%20chances%20of%20entering%20the%20fray%20were%20thus%20spoilt.%20There%20had%20been%20similar%20speculation%20on%20Devendra%20contesting%20the%20elections%20in%202018%20as%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F261500%2Fmadhya-pradesh-elections-union-minister-narendra-singh-tomar-devendra-pratap-viral-video%2F%5C%22%3EHindi%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F261500%2Fmadhya-pradesh-elections-union-minister-narendra-singh-tomar-devendra-pratap-viral-video%2F%5C%22%3Eoriginal%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700041292000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmadhya-pradesh-bjp-narendra-singh-tomar-devendra-viral-video%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Released%20just%20before%20the%20crucial%20state%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20claimed%20that%20these%