their%20students%E2%80%99%20success%2C%20such%20as%20exam%20scores%20or%20certificates%2C%20this%20may%20be%20a%20red%20flag.%20A%20reputable%20coaching%20centre%20should%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20this%20information%20upon%20request%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Check%20for%20accreditation%20or%20certification%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20red%20flag%20that%20he%20suggests%20that%20everyone%20should%20watch%20out%20for%20is%20certification.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20coaching%20centre%20is%20not%20accredited%20or%20certified%20by%20a%20recognised%20organisation%2C%20this%20may%20be%20a%20sign%20that%20they%20are%20not%20meeting%20certain%20standards%20or%20regulations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Lack%20of%20transparency%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20coaching%20centre%20is%20not%20transparent%20about%20its%20teaching%20methods%2C%20course%20materials%2C%20or%20success%20rates%2C%20this%20may%20be%20a%20cause%20for%20concern.%20A%20reputable%20coaching%20centre%20should%20be%20willing%20to%20provide%20this%20information%20to%20prospective%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aakarsh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699627832000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334054%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Searching%20for%20the%20best%20UPSC%20coaching%20institute%3F%20The%20Central%20Consumer%20Protection%20Authority%20(CCPA)%20has%20just%20imposed%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%205%20Lakh%20on%20Khan%20Study%20Group%20(KSG)%20for%20misleading%20ads%20with%20IAS%20toppers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334054%2Fccpa-fines-khan-study-group-how-to-choose-upsc-coaching-centre-in-delhi-ias-toppers%2F%22%2C%22cdn