%20a%20surge%20in%20innovations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20finding%20alternatives%20to%20single-use%20plastics%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F97000%2Fansoo-gupta-one-shoe-trust-responsible-tourism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresponsible%20tourism%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20India%20is%20experiencing%20a%20wave%20of%20cost-effective%20innovations%20in%20nearly%20every%20sector.%20Within%20the%20automobile%20industry%2C%20companies%20have%20introduced%20innovations%20in%20Electric%20Vehicles%20(EVs)%3B%20however%2C%20many%20consumers%20still%20express%20concerns%20over%20its%20battery%20life%2C%20with%20lingering%20anxiety%20about%20reaching%20a%20charging%20point%20or%20their%20destination%20before%20it%20runs%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20Green%20Tiger%20Mobility%20employs%20a%20unique%20model%20which%20enables%20you%20to%20seamlessly%20transition%20between%20petrol%20and%20electric%20power%20within%20the%20same%20vehicle.%20To%20put%20it%20simply%2C%20the%20company%20converts%20your%20conventional%20petrol%20vehicle%20into%20a%20hybrid%20model%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20operate%20on%20both%20petrol%20and%20electric%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20your%20battery%20running%20out%20mid-journey%3B%20you%20can%20easily%20switch%20to%20petrol.%20As%20the%20founder%2C%20Ashish%20Dokania%2C%20aptly%20puts%20it%20for%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20like%20having%20two%20scooters%20in%20one.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20road%20to%20green%20mobility%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Ashish%20Donkaia%20had%20always%20been%20keen%20on%20building%20something%20on%20his%20own.%20Coming%20from%20a%20family%20of%20entrepreneurs%2C%20he%20says%20that%20the%20instin