C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20banyan%20trees%20are%20revered%20as%20symbols%20of%20immortality%20and%20are%20designated%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98National%20Tree%20of%20India%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20four%20years%20later%2C%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20(NGT)%20has%20directed%20NHAI%20to%20conduct%20an%20Environmental%20Impact%20Assessment%20(EIA)%20to%20minimise%20the%20felling%20of%20hundreds%20of%20century-old%20banyan%20trees%20in%20the%20Chevella%20region%20before%20taking%20up%20the%20expansion%20of%20NH%20163%20between%20Hyderabad%20and%20Bijapur%2C%20which%20passes%20through%20Chevella%20in%20Ranga%20Reddy%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20citizens%E2%80%99%20group%20has%20welcomed%20the%20NGT%E2%80%99s%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECitizens%20vs%20NHAI%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20mid-2019%2C%20the%20members%20of%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F312765%2Fhow-to-start-plantation-drive-in-my-city-kolkata-engineer-shares-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecitizens%E2%80%99%20group%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20supported%20by%20around%20300%20individuals%2C%20were%20informed%20that%20about%201%2C000%20banyan%20trees%20were%20to%20be%20chopped%20off%20or%20translocated%20for%20the%20road%20widening%20project.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20one%20who%20intended%20to%20speak%20against%20this%20decision.%20This%20is%20when%20we%20decided%20to%20get%20together%20and%20take%20action%2C%E2%80%9D%20Asiya%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20found%20that%20the%20authorities%20could%20easily%20chop%20off%20trees%20in%20the%20name%20of%20developmental%20project%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20law%20to%20protect%20them.%20However%2C%20we%20found%20a%20loophole.%20The%20NHAI%20did%20not%20conduct%20the%20EIA%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Environment%20Protection%20Act%201986%20mandates%20an%20Environmental%20Impact%20Assessment%20(EIA)%20to%20assess%20damage%20in%20the%20development%20projects%20and%20provide%20a%20plan%20to%20reduce%20the%20negative%20environmental%20effect%20of%20proposed%20development%20projects%20through%20alternative%20approaches%20and%20design%20modification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-6-1699538732.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202019%2C%20a%20group%20of%20about%2020%20citizens%20got%20together%20to%20fight%20the%20authorities%20to%20save%20their%20beloved%20trees.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-6-1699538732.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-6-1699538732-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-6-1699538732-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-6-1699538732-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-6-1699538732-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333948%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202019%2C%20a%20group%20of%20about%2020%20citizens%20got%20together%20to%20fight%20the%20authorities%20to%20save%20their%20beloved%20trees.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20NH%20163%20widening%20project%2C%20the%20NHAI%20did%20not%20look%20into%20alternative%20routes%20and%20conduct%20an%20enumeration%20of%20the%20trees%20affected%2C%20despite%20awarding%20contracts%20for%20developing%20the%20road.%20The%20old%20road%2C%20with%20thousands%20of%20trees%20including%20banyans%20planted%20by%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%20government%2C%20has%20a%20heritage%20value%2C%E2%80%9D%20points%20out%20Natasha%20Ramarathnam%2C%20one%20of%20the%20members%20of%20the%20citizens%E2%80%99%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20banyans%20form%20an%20ecological%20corridor%20connecting%20different%20parts%20of%20Telangana%20state%20for%20many%20birds%20and%20other%20species.%20Neither%20the%20unique%20features%20of%20this%20corridor%20nor%20its%20historic%20value%20were%20addressed.%20In%20an%20era%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20we%20must%20reevaluate%20what%20it%20means%20to%20cut%20down%20trees%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20thousands%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20EIA%20is%20usually%20required%20for%20a%20development%20project%20when%20there%20are%20protected%20areas%20like%20national%20parks%2C%20wildlife%20sanctuaries%2C%20and%20biosphere%20reserves%20in%20the%20project%20area%20of%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20applicants%20in%20the%20NGT%20petition%2C%20Tejah%20Balantrapu%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20trees%20have%20a%20legal%20value%20if%20they%20form%20forests%20and%20reserves%2C%20but%20trees%20lined%20around%20the%20road%20do%20not%20have%20such%20value.%20Essentially%2C%20all%20these%20natural%20landforms%20%E2%80%94%20trees%2C%20rocks%2C%20boulders%2C%20and%20water%20bodies%20%E2%80%94%20are%20looked%20at%20as%20obstacles%20in%20the%20way%20of%20expansion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20reason%2C%20the%2043-year-old%20says%2C%20why%20NHAI%20said%20EIA%20was%20not%20required%20in%20this%20particular%20project.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20said%20that%20EIA%20needed%20to%20be%20conducted%20only%20for%20highway%20projects%20longer%20than%20100%20km.%20And%20since%20this%20stretch%20was%20below%20100%20km%20(46%20km)%2C%20it%20did%20not%20require%20an%20EIA.%20However%2C%20NH-163%20has%20been%20expanded%20before%2C%20again%20in%20small%20stretches%2C%20from%20Warangal%20to%20Hyderabad.%20As%20a%20result%20of%20this%20segmentation%2C%20the%20full%20length%20of%20the%20highway%20escapes%20the%20rule%20of%20assessment%20for%20impact%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20as%20per%20Indian%20Road%20Congress%20(IRC)%20guidelines%2C%20NHAI%20needs%20to%20incorporate%20natural%20landscape%20in%20road%20design.%20Besides%2C%20these%20banyan%20trees%20in%20thousands%20act%20as%20a%20corridor%20for%20several%20species%20like%20hornbills%20and%20have%20their%20own%20ecosystem.%20If%20these%20trees%20are%20axed%2C%20where%20will%20these%20species%20go%3F%E2%80%9D%20asks%20Tejah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-3-1699537078.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20citizens%20have%20geotagged%20914%20banyans%20on%20the%2046.6%20km%20stretch.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-3-1699537078.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-3-1699537078-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-3-1699537078-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-3-1699537078-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fbanyan-3-1699537078-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333923%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20citizens%20have%20geotagged%20914%20banyans%20on%20the%2046.6%20km%20stretch.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGeotagging%20Chevella%20banyans%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20absence%20of%20precise%20documentation%20on%20the%20number%20of%20banyan%20trees%20in%20the%20stretch%20that%20were%20at%20risk%2C%20the%20group%20also%20conducted%20an%20exercise%20to%20geotag%20all%20the%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20GPS%20locator%20applications%2C%20they%20geotagged%20and%20photographed%20all%20the%20Chevella%20banyans%20in%20June%202022.%20It%20took%20them%20four%20days%20to%20complete%20the%20exercise.%20The%20data%20came%20out%20to%20be%20for%20914%20banyans%20on%20the%2046.6%20km%20stretch%2C%20which%20was%20lower%20than%20what%20the%20authorities%20quoted%20(749)%2C%20informs%20Natasha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20this%20database%2C%20we%20could%20counter%20the%20claims%20of%20NHAI%20that%20these%20were%20very%20small%20and%20stunted%20trees%20and%20it%20would%20be%20no%20loss%20if%20they%20were%20axed.%20What%20we%20took%20to%20NGT%20was%20not%20just%20an%20emotional%20appeal%20but%20actually%20data%20backed%20with%20facts%20and%20figures.%20Also%2C%20anyone%20can%20replicate%20this%20method%20with%20little%20effort%20to%20geo-tag%20trees%20in%20their%20cities%20and%20hold%20authorities%20accountable%20when%20healthy%20trees%20are%20made%20to%20disappear%20overnight%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20citizens%E2%80%99%20group%20also%20sought%20help%20from%20several%20ministers%2C%20Members%20of%20Parliament%20(MPs)%2C%20and%20Members%20of%20the%20Legislative%20Assembly%20(MLAs)%2C%20Asiya%20says.%20But%20when%20no%20one%20in%20power%20listened%20to%20them%2C%20they%20approached%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20and%20filed%20a%20petition%20against%20the%20decision%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20three%20citizens%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Natasha%2C%20Pranay%20Juvvadi%2C%20and%20Tejah%20%E2%80%94%20became%20applicants%20in%20the%20case%2C%20the%20remaining%20citizens%20kept%20organising%20awareness%20campaigns%20across%20the%20city%20