as%20diagnosed%20with%20cerebral%20palsy%2C%20a%20neurological%20condition%20that%20affects%20movement%20and%20muscle%20coordination.%20He%20had%20to%20be%20taken%20for%20physiotherapy%20daily%20since%20then.%20As%20Ravindra%20was%20working%20in%20a%20bank%2C%20Sujata%20took%20on%20this%20responsibility.%20She%20would%20carry%20her%20month-old%20baby%20%E2%80%94%20who%20hardly%20weighed%20a%20kilo%20%E2%80%94%20from%20Badlapur%20to%20Parel%20everyday%20for%20therapy%2C%20in%20hopes%20of%20providing%20him%20with%20a%20chance%20to%20have%20a%20better%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20journey%20of%20the%20mother%20and%20son%20continued%20for%20the%20first%20seven%20years%20of%20his%20life.%20But%20these%20daily%20train%20rides%20while%20lifting%20a%20young%20boy%20were%20taxing%20for%20Sujata%2C%20who%20is%2061%20today.%20She%20knew%20that%20there%20was%20a%20better%20way%3B%20there%20had%20to%20be%20a%20better%20way%20to%20help%20her%20son.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20found%20our%20calling%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20853px)%20100vw%2C%20853px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango3-1699455859.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Children%20are%20engaged%20in%20art%2C%20craft%2C%20games%20and%20other%20activities%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango3-1699455859.jpeg%20853w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango3-1699455859-200x300.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango3-1699455859-500x750.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango3-1699455859-768x1152.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango3-1699455859-150x225.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333889%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChildren%20are%20engaged%20in%20art%2C%20craft%2C%20games%20and%20other%20activities%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Sujata%20recalls%20the%20initial%20few%20years.%20While%20she%20had%20to%20take%20Akshay%20to%20KEM%20for%20the%20first%202.5%20years%20for%20therapy%2C%20she%20later%20enrolled%20him%20at%20Spastics%20Society%2C%20Bandra%2C%20as%20local%20schools%20refused%20to%20admit%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20I%20would%20leave%20home%20at%207%20am%2C%20reach%20Spastics%20at%209%20am%20for%20his%20schooling.%20After%20that%2C%20I%20would%20take%20him%20to%20Haji%20Ali%20to%20a%20place%20that%20offered%20physiotherapy%20and%20speech%20and%20occupational%20therapy%20under%20one%20roof%20which%20got%20over%20by%204%3A30%20pm.%20I%20would%20reach%20home%20by%206%20pm.%20This%20was%20my%20routine%20six%20days%20a%20week%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Sujata.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20Akshay%20can%E2%80%99t%20walk%2C%20she%20had%20to%20lift%20him.%20Travelling%20in%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20fast%20and%20unforgiving%20local%20trains%20at%20peak%20times%20with%20a%20child%20is%20no%20mean%20feat.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20this%20led%20to%20back%20pain%20and%20other%20health%20problems%20for%20Sujata.%20She%20saw%20at%20the%20therapy%20centre%20that%20she%20was%20not%20alone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20many%20parents%20from%20underprivileged%20backgrounds%20who%20brought%20their%20children%20to%20therapy.%20Many%20had%20to%20discontinue%20as%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20it%20and%20the%20travel%20was%20too%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESujata%20realised%20that%20if%20they%20had%20a%20centre%20which%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%