ining%2C%20physiotherapy%2C%20round%20the%20clock%20care%2C%20a%20mini-hospital%2C%20a%20doctor%2C%20a%20psychiatrist%2C%20a%20nurse%20and%20an%20ambulance.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20access%20to%20vast%20open%20areas%2C%20their%20residents%20participate%20in%20games%2C%20yoga%20and%20other%20activities%20with%20gusto.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSee%2C%20many%20parents%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20resources%20to%20handle%20such%20children%2C%20often%20abandoning%20them.%20We%20are%20providing%20an%20avenue%20for%20such%20children%20to%20really%20flourish%20and%20do%20their%20best.%20Parents%2C%20too%2C%20can%20be%20satisfied%20that%20their%20children%20are%20doing%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Ravindra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2062-year-old%20says%20that%20the%20initial%20few%20years%20of%20raising%20Akshay%20was%20challenging.%20He%20felt%20depressed%2C%20he%20admits%2C%20thinking%20about%20what%20would%20happen%20to%20him%20in%20the%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWho%20will%20take%20care%20of%20him%20after%20us%3F%20This%20question%20plagues%20the%20mind%20of%20every%20parent%20of%20a%20disabled%20child.%20We%20have%20built%20this%20as%20a%20solution%20to%20that.%20I%20felt%20positive%20after%20building%20Sangopita.%20Akshay%20is%20also%20doing%20much%20better%20and%20has%20developed%20well%20in%20these%20surroundings%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGiving%20them%20wings%20to%20fly%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201498px)%20100vw%2C%201498px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango2-min-1699456529.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221498%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22There%20are%2062%20children%20in%20Sangopita%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsango2-min-1699456529.jpeg%201498w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%